00:16:34,600 --> 00:16:35,380
 recenziju.

460
00:16:35,380 --> 00:16:36,740
 Da se sitit.

461
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:38,420
 I o meni posla,

462
00:16:38,420 --> 00:16:38,860
 naprijed,

463
00:16:38,860 --> 00:16:39,420
 kada sam prošla,

464
00:16:39,420 --> 00:16:40,480
 posla naprijed upitnik,

465
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:40,680
 ono,

466
00:16:40,680 --> 00:16:41,100
 sa ne znam,

467
00:16:41,100 --> 00:16:41,820
 baje spitalja,

468
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:42,360
 da govorim na to,

469
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:42,880
 pa ću on naslovno

470
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:43,940
 dogaj pisat recenziju.

471
00:16:43,940 --> 00:16:46,000
 Što imaš duple tekstove?

472
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:47,320
 Pa mislim se,

473
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:48,480
 pa kako ću izdvojit,

474
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:49,360
 koji mi je bolji

475
00:16:49,360 --> 00:16:50,240
 kad su mi oba,

476
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:51,700
 meni se oba puno značila,

477
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:53,940
 a i vidi sa razlika

478
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:54,920
 da nije isti čovjek,

479
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:55,140
 ono,

480
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:56,400
 da im vidi sa napredak neki,

481
00:16:56,400 --> 00:16:57,420
 pa nek ljudi to osjete.

482
00:16:57,420 --> 00:16:58,480
 Ne,

483
00:16:58,480 --> 00:16:59,660
 izaberi sama jedan.

484
00:16:59,660 --> 00:17:00,460
 Kako je,

485
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:01,420
 to je bila teško,

486
00:17:01,420 --> 00:17:02,560
 te rezove raditi.

487
00:17:02,560 --> 00:17:04,420
 Pa onda sam išao random,

488
00:17:04,420 --> 00:17:06,240
 pročitao onako naslovnice,

489
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:06,460
 ja sam,

490
00:17:06,460 --> 00:17:06,740
 aha,

491
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:07,760
 ova mi se sad ne sviđa,

492
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:08,080
 danas mi se,

493
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:08,960
 danas mi ovaj nije dobar,

494
00:17:08,960 --> 00:17:09,640
 delete.

495
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:11,340
 I tako sam radio,

496
00:17:11,340 --> 00:17:12,940
 tako je bruto ljudi

497
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:13,640
 koji je spomagali

498
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:15,040
 da kod ti četvrho framaša,

499
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:16,380
 Mislav,

500
00:17:16,380 --> 00:17:16,960
 Andreja,

501
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:17,960
 Iva i Nino,

502
00:17:22,740 --> 00:17:24,960
 da nije negavirana knjiga

503
00:17:24,960 --> 00:17:26,140
 bi bila potpuno drugačija,

504
00:17:26,140 --> 00:17:26,540
 tako da,

505
00:17:26,540 --> 00:17:27,220
 hvala njemu.

506
00:17:27,220 --> 00:17:29,120
 Onda je tu,

507
00:17:29,120 --> 00:17:30,580
 postupio naših ognješta,

508
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:31,340
 koje je nekim svojim

509
00:17:31,340 --> 00:17:32,060
 stručnim sajetima

510
00:17:32,060 --> 00:17:33,000
 za neke druge stvari,

511
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:33,600
 za osmirenje,

512
00:17:33,600 --> 00:17:34,660
 pomoglo,

513
00:17:34,660 --> 00:17:35,200
 ovaj,

514
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:35,460
 da se,

515
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:37,020
 gdje knjiga dođe do ovoga,

516
00:17:37,020 --> 00:17:39,740
 za naslovnicu,

517
00:17:39,740 --> 00:17:40,680
 je zaslužan,

518
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:41,120
 dakle,

519
00:17:41,120 --> 00:17:42,240
 Zravko Terkeš,

520
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,500
 koji je napravio

521
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:44,540
 jako fin posao.

522
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:45,340
 Ono,

523
00:17:45,340 --> 00:17:46,420
 na prvi pukaj je poslao,

524
00:17:46,420 --> 00:17:46,940
 samo smo rekli,

525
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:47,400
 to je to,

526
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:47,960
 uopće nije,

527
00:17:48,220 --> 00:17:48,940
 nije bilo potrebno

528
00:17:48,940 --> 00:17:51,280
 da tražemo druga rješenja.

529
00:17:51,280 --> 00:17:52,680
 Da naslovnica baš odaje

530
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:53,700
 neki snažan dojav.

531
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:54,340
 Dakle,

532
00:17:54,340 --> 00:17:55,260
 tu je cesta,

533
00:17:55,260 --> 00:17:57,540
 put kojim idem za Bogom

534
00:17:57,540 --> 00:17:58,720
 i križ koji obilježava

535
00:17:58,720 --> 00:17:59,340
 taj put.

536
00:17:59,340 --> 00:17:59,780
 Jednostavno,

537
00:17:59,780 --> 00:18:00,720
 tu je sve,

538
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,020
 a nema gdje je zoliko

539
00:18:02,020 --> 00:18:02,700
 da cesta vodi.

540
00:18:02,700 --> 00:18:05,240
 Tako da,

541
00:18:05,240 --> 00:18:06,360
 sve je rekao.

542
00:18:06,360 --> 00:18:07,820
 Tu smo baš,

543
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:08,940
 i on i ja smo ostali,

544
00:18:08,940 --> 00:18:09,680
 pa on kaže

545
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,600
 da nam nije ljepšu stvar

546
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:11,560
 u životu napravio.

547
00:18:11,560 --> 00:18:13,340
 Ja sam se samo složio s time.

548
00:18:13,340 --> 00:18:14,060
 Baš je,

549
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:15,080
 na prvi dojam,

550
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:16,000
 na prvi pogled,

551
00:18:16,940 --> 00:18:18,120
 nemao više ništa.

552
00:18:18,120 --> 00:18:19,620
 Ima li neke tajne

553
00:18:19,620 --> 00:18:20,420
 za naslova,

554
00:18:20,420 --> 00:18:21,600
 učitelju za to,

555
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:23,120
 bo on će u kamo god ti pošao?

556
00:18:23,120 --> 00:18:24,340
 Pa tajni nema.

557
00:18:24,340 --> 00:18:24,600
 Mislim,

558
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:25,700
 onaj ko me zna dugo,

559
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:27,400
 zna da me te riječi

560
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,640
 prate odavno,

561
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,640
 još od prije mlade emisije,

562
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:31,520
 koje su tek za mlado,

563
00:18:31,520 --> 00:18:33,200
 mi su ljudi to prvi put skontar,

564
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:33,780
 sam to stavio

565
00:18:33,780 --> 00:18:34,880
 kamo da misničko geslo,

566
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:36,880
 ali su se meni urezale

567
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:38,920
 u pamet na trećoj godine teologije.

568
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:41,460
 Do tada su mi bile riječi,

569
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:42,540
 dajte im vijesti.

570
00:18:42,540 --> 00:18:45,640
 O njima sam jako puno razmišljao,

571
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:47,040
 do taj trećeg godine teologije.

572
00:18:47,040 --> 00:18:48,080
 Tam je rečenica,

573
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:48,460
 odavikuju,

574
00:18:48,460 --> 00:18:49,700
 nekako ljekivala ušima,

575
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:51,280
 ali te sam godine

576
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:52,400
 na ovu rečenicu

577
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:54,500
 čuo na neki drugačiji način,

578
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:55,560
 ne zna ni ja zašto,

579
00:18:55,560 --> 00:18:56,800
 ali jednostavno,

580
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:57,280
 djekljeno,

581
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:58,220
 polpuno drugačiji,

582
00:18:58,220 --> 00:19:00,400
 omeni više me nije pušljala na miru.

583
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,800
 ne prestane razmišljati o tome,

584
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:03,420
 to baš mi je bio izazov,

585
00:19:03,420 --> 00:19:04,840
 neka postane teretna.

586
00:19:04,840 --> 00:19:07,500
 Tako da nisam se dugo mislio

587
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:08,620
 koji će biti naslov,

588
00:19:08,620 --> 00:19:10,440
 kad jako puno tekstova

589
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,160
 završava tim riječima

590
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:14,000
 i većina tekstova govori

591
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:16,660
 na koje bi iti upravo o tim riječima,

592
00:19:16,660 --> 00:19:17,880
 kako iti za Bogom.

593
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,620
 pun padova,

594
00:19:19,620 --> 00:19:20,720
 pun nekih, ne znam nija,

595
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:21,420
 i kriza,

596
00:19:21,420 --> 00:19:22,740
 i teških trenutaka,

597
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:23,780
 i mraka,

598
00:19:23,780 --> 00:19:25,520
 i nade,

599
00:19:25,520 --> 00:19:27,060
 i svega nečega i dobroga,

600
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:29,060
 a kako unotor svemu tome

601
00:19:29,060 --> 00:19:30,140
 nastaviti ići za njim.

602
00:19:30,140 --> 00:19:31,700
 Tamo gdje ne znaš

603
00:19:31,700 --> 00:19:32,740
 šta te čeka apsolutno.

604
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:34,300
 Iđeš upoznaš stranca,

605
00:19:34,300 --> 00:19:35,620
 ne znaš nikoj njih,

606
00:19:35,620 --> 00:19:36,040
 šta je s njim,

607
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:37,140
 djeliš sve šta imaš,

608
00:19:37,140 --> 00:19:39,420
 ono postane ti prijatelj.

609
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:40,500
 Zato što si išao za Bogom

610
00:19:40,500 --> 00:19:42,020
 koji te čekao u tom strancu.

611
00:19:42,020 --> 00:19:44,960
 Tako da se mi te riječi nekako,

612
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:50,480
 kada Mladić dolazi do Isusa.

613
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:51,520
 Bogat Mladić dolazi do Isusa,

614
00:19:51,520 --> 00:19:53,080
 a naš vlast nije pošao za Isusom.

615
00:19:53,080 --> 00:19:54,940
 Tužan se vratio kući.

616
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:57,860
 Ne da želim to ispraviti,

617
00:19:57,860 --> 00:20:00,120
 nego vidi li mi te riječi puno znače,

618
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:01,840
 ali ću uspopraviti to,

619
00:20:01,840 --> 00:20:04,280
 mogu zasvoju život za njegov,

620
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:05,620
 ne znam šta je kasnije biglo,

621
00:20:05,620 --> 00:20:07,340
 ali zasvoju sam odgovoran,

622
00:20:07,340 --> 00:20:08,980
 tako da nekako sam uzelao to za sebi

623
00:20:08,980 --> 00:20:10,620
 za program života te riječi,

624
00:20:10,620 --> 00:20:12,060
 pa ti god,

625
00:20:12,060 --> 00:20:13,920
 tu ću, pa šta god.

626
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:16,300
 Gospodino, pozi prema njima,

627
00:20:16,380 --> 00:20:18,640
 kako je izgledao tvoj put i pozi.

628
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:20,700
 Mislim, to je naravno vezano

629
00:20:20,700 --> 00:20:22,100
 svakog pojedinca osobno,

630
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:25,080
 svakog bog zove na njegov osoba način,

631
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:27,260
 ali evo kako je tvoj put izgledao.

632
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:29,340
 Pa ne mogu reći da je bilo neki,

633
00:20:29,340 --> 00:20:31,380
 ne znam, paluski trenutak

634
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:32,480
 kada sam pao s konja,

635
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:34,340
 ne znam, osliplu me pa nešto vidio,

636
00:20:34,340 --> 00:20:36,120
 čuo, doživio, na takav način.

637
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:39,780
 Ne mogu reći da je da ima neki takih stvari,

638
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:42,300
 ali dok sam bio djete,

639
00:20:42,300 --> 00:20:43,840
 još ono,

640
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:46,620
 dolazim iz tradicionalne katoličke obitelji

641
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:48,700
 gdje se uvijek Boga moli mater,

642
00:20:48,700 --> 00:20:51,560
 nepristano pelila da Boga moramo moliti zajedno

643
00:20:51,560 --> 00:20:53,980
 i sam i svakog večer sa Boga moli u kući

644
00:20:53,980 --> 00:20:55,960
 i malo prema ter poslala poruku u grupu

645
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:57,140
 a u djedica molit ćemo Boga.

646
00:20:57,140 --> 00:21:00,160
 To je baš svakog večer bilo.

647
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:02,200
 Naravno, bilo je tu jako puno problema u obitelji,

648
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:04,460
 a moja obitelj nije idealna.

649
00:21:04,460 --> 00:21:05,300
 Daleko od toga.

650
00:21:05,300 --> 00:21:07,400
 Daleko od toga sam idealna obitelj,

651
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:09,700
 ali ne sam mama naučila da se u sve mu uzdamo u Boga.

652
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:14,260
 i u svom siromaštu u kojeg je bilo i u problemima i ovome i onome,

653
00:21:14,260 --> 00:21:18,440
 u sve mu ubi gledaju uboga i prita ono što od njegov gledaju da ne bit će dobro.

654
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:19,780
 I tako nam je stvarno bilo.

655
00:21:21,780 --> 00:21:25,220
 Mama nam je rekla da se upriješamo na ministrante.

656
00:21:25,220 --> 00:21:28,680
 Meni i braći, najstariji nikad nije pošla tu stvar.

657
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:30,240
 Kako vas ima u uči obitelji?

658
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:31,300
 Osmero djece.

659
00:21:31,300 --> 00:21:34,020
 Naš četvorca braća idemo godinu za godinu,

660
00:21:34,020 --> 00:21:36,220
 pa dvi sestre, pa brat pa sestra.

661
00:21:36,220 --> 00:21:40,120
 Upisujem svoj ministrante nakon prve priče,

662
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:42,320
 ste prije nije moglo, pa smo tada krenuli.

663
00:21:43,780 --> 00:21:49,220
 I tu sam kroz ministrante upoznaš malo pobliže život fratara.

664
00:21:49,220 --> 00:21:51,080
 Ne moraš ti puno pohvatati dite si.

665
00:21:51,080 --> 00:21:52,680
 Vidiš neke stvari s oltara.

666
00:21:52,680 --> 00:21:55,760
 U sakristi popričaš s fratom, bacioš dekoj u foru

667
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:58,520
 i to to što ćeš ti ući za neki život fratara.

668
00:21:58,520 --> 00:22:01,520
 Eventalno ako nešto treba pomoć od rata, kod crkve,

669
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:03,360
 dok ste vi svi tu, a to ja,

670
00:22:03,360 --> 00:22:05,520
 ali malo ti ko dite toga moraš svariti.

671
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:08,660
 I dok si ustavi oltar nekako bio,

672
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:10,740
 zamiješljaš nekad sebe.

673
00:22:11,380 --> 00:22:13,600
 Ne je nužno da se tu već rodio poziv,

674
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:15,440
 ali bila je ta neka želja prisutna,

675
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:17,360
 ono, ću mogu bi ja nekad,

676
00:22:17,360 --> 00:22:20,920
 ali nisam o tome ko dite nikad razmišljao.

677
00:22:20,920 --> 00:22:23,120
 Imao sam potpuno drugačije želje,

678
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:24,400
 biti astronaut, recimo,

679
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:26,440
 s tomo mi je dugo vremena bilo da budem astronaut.

680
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:28,600
 Kasnije u srednjoj školi,

681
00:22:28,600 --> 00:22:32,320
 ono, volio bi biti profesor matematike i fizike,

682
00:22:32,320 --> 00:22:34,400
 to mi je baš bila želja,

683
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,480
 o tome sam baš uživo,

684
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:36,880
 držao sam instrukcije,

685
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:37,960
 pa me to bila baš ono,

686
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,820
 to me je baš uvijek veselo.

687
00:22:40,140 --> 00:22:41,860
 Pa sam to volio postat.

688
00:22:41,860 --> 00:22:45,320
 Šta je bilo još na popisu za državnu maturu,

689
00:22:45,320 --> 00:22:46,640
 zrakoplovstvo,

690
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:47,940
 fizioterapija,

691
00:22:47,940 --> 00:22:49,540
 grafički dizajn,

692
00:22:49,540 --> 00:22:50,860
 elektrotehnika,

693
00:22:50,860 --> 00:22:51,400
 strojačnost,

694
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:52,580
 znači nema šta nije bilo,

695
00:22:52,580 --> 00:22:53,400
 a sve me je zanimalo.

696
00:22:53,400 --> 00:22:55,360
 Šta si upisao?

697
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:57,320
 Elektrotehniku,

698
00:22:57,460 --> 00:23:00,680
 da se vratimo mi na priču o tom pozivu.

699
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:04,460
 Moja obitelj,

700
00:23:04,460 --> 00:23:05,020
 da prav mama,

701
00:23:05,020 --> 00:23:06,740
 nas je kao djecu

702
00:23:06,740 --> 00:23:08,140
 vodila u Međugorje često.

703
00:23:08,140 --> 00:23:11,360
 Ovo nisam nisam nigdje pričao.

704
00:23:11,360 --> 00:23:13,020
 Ona se često vodila u Međugorje,

705
00:23:13,020 --> 00:23:13,640
 kad bi got mogla,

706
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:14,480
 ona nije vozila,

707
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,080
 jedno vrijeme,

708
00:23:15,080 --> 00:23:17,800
 kad bi se mogli nekomu baciti auto ili pješke,

709
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:18,860
 kad su mogli ići vodila,

710
00:23:18,860 --> 00:23:20,000
 nas je pješke u Međugorje.

711
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:22,280
 To je korisla svaku priliku,

712
00:23:22,280 --> 00:23:22,880
 baš ono.

713
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:24,920
 I tamo,

714
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,420
 za vrijeme nekog seminara,

715
00:23:26,420 --> 00:23:28,260
 su se omeni rađale neke ideje,

716
00:23:28,260 --> 00:23:29,300
 već iznutra,

717
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:32,000
 koje ja nisam znao nikome reći.

718
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:34,720
 To baš nikome nije saznao.

719
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:36,100
 Do nedavno,

720
00:23:36,100 --> 00:23:37,200
 jedna častna sestra,

721
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:38,680
 koja je kasnije otišla u Klarise.

722
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:40,880
 Tako da ostaće u njoj,

723
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:42,220
 znamo ona i ja.

724
00:23:42,220 --> 00:23:45,280
 Ali neke se stvari rađale u meni,

725
00:23:45,280 --> 00:23:46,420
 koje nisam znao reći nikom,

726
00:23:46,420 --> 00:23:47,500
 pa sam to osobi čuva,

727
00:23:47,500 --> 00:23:48,520
 i to je tako ostalo.

728
00:23:48,520 --> 00:23:50,500
 Među remenu se opisujem

729
00:23:50,500 --> 00:23:52,060
 na framu u osmom razredu,

730
00:23:52,060 --> 00:23:54,360
 malo u framu upoznajem sve tog franja.

731
00:23:54,360 --> 00:23:56,920
 Tog lika koji mi je bio,

732
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:59,780
 slušaš o svecu koji je radio sve i svašta.

733
00:23:59,780 --> 00:24:02,020
 Od gluposti dok je bio mlad,

734
00:24:02,020 --> 00:24:05,320
 želje za ovakvim životom da živi,

735
00:24:05,320 --> 00:24:07,760
 ne znam, nija ko kakav bojem,

736
00:24:07,760 --> 00:24:08,700
 ko kakav bekrija,

737
00:24:08,700 --> 00:24:10,340
 čovjek je uživao u derneku.

738
00:24:10,340 --> 00:24:12,540
 I odjedno on se smiri.

739
00:24:12,540 --> 00:24:14,600
 Šta ti bi čovječe?

740
00:24:14,600 --> 00:24:17,220
 U nas kontrašta je bio prosjev Boži

741
00:24:17,220 --> 00:24:19,120
 u njegovoj duši da se dogodi nešto veliko.

742
00:24:20,280 --> 00:24:21,280
 ono čovječe moćna,

743
00:24:21,280 --> 00:24:22,580
 baš moćna stvar.

744
00:24:22,580 --> 00:24:24,880
 Ja odem u prvi razred,

745
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:26,520
 da upišem se u tu veliku framu.

746
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:28,580
 Poznaš Franju malo dublj,

747
00:24:28,580 --> 00:24:29,980
 ali nisam to veli sadoželjavao

748
00:24:29,980 --> 00:24:30,980
 ko mogu obija u frate,

749
00:24:30,980 --> 00:24:32,620
 sam mi se Franju kao Franju svidio.

750
00:24:33,080 --> 00:24:35,380
 Daleko je tu bila još ideja da postanem stvarno fratar.

751
00:24:35,380 --> 00:24:38,920
 Tek odlazkom u drugi razred,

752
00:24:38,920 --> 00:24:41,560
 moj mlađi brat Bože

753
00:24:41,560 --> 00:24:42,900
 odlazi u prvi razred,

754
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:44,200
 u sve mi je ništo visoko.

755
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:47,080
 To mi je bio prvi proces za razmišljanje.

756
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:49,560
 Ako more Bože, što ne biti?

757
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:50,780
 Što tebi fali?

758
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:52,680
 Ništa.

759
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:54,080
 Živ, zravku.

760
00:24:54,080 --> 00:24:54,660
 Mislim,

761
00:24:54,660 --> 00:24:55,740
 u glavi nisam,

762
00:24:55,740 --> 00:24:56,560
 ali jel?

763
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:58,960
 Što tebi fali?

764
00:24:58,960 --> 00:24:59,940
 Možeš iti otići.

765
00:24:59,940 --> 00:25:01,140
 Ali neko gotovo,

766
00:25:01,140 --> 00:25:02,740
 već sam gimnazio poslu,

767
00:25:02,780 --> 00:25:04,040
 nema sam smislila da se prekidam

768
00:25:04,040 --> 00:25:04,980
 pa da mu fratre, ono.

769
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:07,200
 A je moj si imala za mene neke druge planove

770
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:08,780
 da upišem dobar fakultetima,

771
00:25:08,780 --> 00:25:09,720
 finu ženu,

772
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:10,520
 dobru firmu,

773
00:25:10,520 --> 00:25:11,840
 da pomažem svoju obitelj.

774
00:25:11,840 --> 00:25:13,560
 Nemam ništa patog toga,

775
00:25:13,560 --> 00:25:14,200
 daleko od toga.

776
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:15,780
 Voleo bi im pomagati.

777
00:25:15,780 --> 00:25:17,920
 Clementa je lijepa želja.

778
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:19,680
 Uzvratnjima za svu muku,

779
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:21,580
 koju su podnijeli za svu nas,

780
00:25:21,580 --> 00:25:22,380
 za sve nas dicu.

781
00:25:22,380 --> 00:25:24,400
 Najmalje što mogu je uzvratiti,

782
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:26,240
 ima što ću im nekad nešto dati po sudi,

783
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:26,920
 ne znam, nebitno.

784
00:25:27,840 --> 00:25:29,660
 To mi je bila fina implementa želja,

785
00:25:29,660 --> 00:25:31,060
 ali se tu ubacio Bog,

786
00:25:31,060 --> 00:25:32,140
 time što me 2009.

787
00:25:32,140 --> 00:25:33,820
 na kraju mog drugog srednje

788
00:25:33,820 --> 00:25:35,700
 odveo u Asis,

789
00:25:35,700 --> 00:25:36,880
 s ramom Hercegovina.

790
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,620
 Tu uspočeo od Belaj.

791
00:25:38,620 --> 00:25:41,660
 Ulazim u porcijunkulu,

792
00:25:41,660 --> 00:25:45,100
 ne razmišljajući o čemu.

793
00:25:45,100 --> 00:25:46,780
 Dakle, nisam otišao u Asis,

794
00:25:46,780 --> 00:25:47,560
 da meni Bog kažeo

795
00:25:47,560 --> 00:25:48,680
 da trebali ja bi fratr.

796
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:50,560
 Nisam ja to govorio,

797
00:25:50,560 --> 00:25:51,740
 fratr ili prijateljima.

798
00:25:51,740 --> 00:25:53,300
 To niko, dakle, nije znao

799
00:25:53,300 --> 00:25:55,440
 da je meni se to barem pojavljivalo

800
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:56,860
 nekad u duši ili u mislima.

801
00:25:56,980 --> 00:25:57,940
 to niko nije znao.

802
00:25:57,940 --> 00:26:00,060
 I ulazim u porcijunkulu

803
00:26:00,060 --> 00:26:02,140
 samo da se pomolim.

804
00:26:02,140 --> 00:26:03,480
 Niti ja znam šta ću molit,

805
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:04,180
 kako ću molit,

806
00:26:04,180 --> 00:26:04,740
 ni šta se molit.

807
00:26:04,740 --> 00:26:05,860
 Znam da se tu možeš dobiti oprost.

808
00:26:05,860 --> 00:26:08,120
 Bila sam išao tamo molit oprost.

809
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:10,260
 I izlazim vanka

810
00:26:10,260 --> 00:26:11,700
 iz one male porcijunkule

811
00:26:11,700 --> 00:26:13,920
 i meni samo u glavi

812
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:14,580
 gdje koju riječ

813
00:26:14,580 --> 00:26:15,700
 ti ćeš biti fratr,

814
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:16,880
 ti ćeš biti fratr,

815
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:17,900
 ti ćeš...

816
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:19,020
 Svim se u sebi davno,

817
00:26:19,020 --> 00:26:19,640
 našta ti je.

818
00:26:19,640 --> 00:26:21,080
 Ota šta je Boža,

819
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:22,020
 ne moraš sad i ti.

820
00:26:22,020 --> 00:26:23,880
 To su ta jedan iskući.

821
00:26:23,980 --> 00:26:27,580
 Nek se nastavi prezime,

822
00:26:27,580 --> 00:26:28,420
 nek se loza nastavlja.

823
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:32,060
 I to isto nisam nikome rekao

824
00:26:32,060 --> 00:26:33,460
 da se to u mene pojavljilo.

825
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:35,520
 To da sam uvijek šutio o sebi.

826
00:26:35,520 --> 00:26:37,420
 Nisam se povjerao

827
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:38,100
 baš ljudima,

828
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:39,480
 ni u obitelji,

829
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:40,300
 ni prijateljima,

830
00:26:40,300 --> 00:26:40,980
 ni naframi,

831
00:26:40,980 --> 00:26:41,720
 ni fratrima.

832
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:45,000
 jednostavno nisam osjećao

833
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:45,660
 ni da treba,

834
00:26:45,660 --> 00:26:47,200
 nisam imao neko upovjerenje.

835
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:49,160
 Ne znam zašto takav sam jednostavno bil.

836
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:54,540
 Ja završavam treći i srednje,

837
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:56,260
 kasnije moj prijatelj,

838
00:26:56,260 --> 00:26:57,320
 tada jako dobar,

839
00:26:57,320 --> 00:26:59,040
 završio i četvrti i srednje.

840
00:26:59,040 --> 00:27:01,640
 Ono da je u fratr.

841
00:27:03,640 --> 00:27:06,720
 srce mi skače i ja bi s tobom,

842
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:07,900
 ali sam tek četvrti raz.

843
00:27:07,900 --> 00:27:09,240
 Ja sam tada on je prvi koji je saznat

844
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:10,160
 da o tome razmišljam.

845
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:13,180
 Ja to s njim podijelim.

846
00:27:13,180 --> 00:27:14,080
 Ono pa super,

847
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:17,580
 otmo je sam baš dugo i fino pričali.

848
00:27:17,580 --> 00:27:22,200
 On je otišao,

849
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:23,920
 ali me žremenu brzo i napustio.

850
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,900
 Koja je meni to tuga bila?

851
00:27:25,900 --> 00:27:27,920
 Moj prijatelj je otišao u fratr

852
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:28,840
 i vratio se kući.

853
00:27:28,840 --> 00:27:30,300
 Šta ako se ja vratim kući?

854
00:27:30,300 --> 00:27:33,060
 Onda zbog toga nisam mogu

855
00:27:33,060 --> 00:27:34,120
 ni reć ni svojima,

856
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,200
 da ja to ne mislim.

857
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:37,740
 Fratru,

858
00:27:37,740 --> 00:27:39,560
 on je već nešto bio slutio,

859
00:27:39,560 --> 00:27:40,320
 vjer je mi ono,

860
00:27:40,320 --> 00:27:41,480
 spomljenim par puta

861
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:42,740
 mogla piti u fratr,

862
00:27:42,740 --> 00:27:44,360
 ali ja bi ono sam to odmanio rukom

863
00:27:44,360 --> 00:27:45,120
 i to je to ono,

864
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:46,200
 ja tada s turama bio

865
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:47,520
 manim za čovječ.

866
00:27:47,520 --> 00:27:48,440
 Ja turama pijes mi piše

867
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:49,460
 njegovjeđenu u fratre.

868
00:27:49,460 --> 00:27:51,320
 Neka hvala reko.

869
00:27:51,320 --> 00:27:54,860
 Nisam bio spreman to

870
00:27:54,860 --> 00:27:56,380
 priznati sebi,

871
00:27:56,380 --> 00:27:57,440
 kamal drugome.

872
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:59,800
 Na kraju četvrtog,

873
00:27:59,800 --> 00:28:00,280
 srednje,

874
00:28:00,280 --> 00:28:02,820
 već ste badomiti odluku.

875
00:28:02,980 --> 00:28:04,620
 meni srce iskačeo,

876
00:28:04,620 --> 00:28:05,460
 želja je da probam

877
00:28:05,460 --> 00:28:06,300
 otići u fratre.

878
00:28:06,300 --> 00:28:07,140
 Ja se brata među vremena

879
00:28:07,140 --> 00:28:08,340
 vratio iz samostana,

880
00:28:08,340 --> 00:28:10,380
 vratio se ono iz sjemeništa,

881
00:28:10,380 --> 00:28:12,060
 upisao gimnaziju,

882
00:28:12,060 --> 00:28:13,060
 poslušio je ono,

883
00:28:13,060 --> 00:28:14,680
 nastavio svoje živo dalje.

884
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:16,180
 Znači ja mogu otići sada,

885
00:28:17,280 --> 00:28:18,640
 ali ne mogu ga mater reći.

886
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:20,760
 Jer mater ima taj plan,

887
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:21,880
 da imam ženu,

888
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:22,380
 dicu,

889
00:28:22,380 --> 00:28:23,120
 dobru firmu,

890
00:28:23,120 --> 00:28:23,880
 pomažem njima.

891
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:25,240
 To je fina želja,

892
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:25,780
 zašto ne?

893
00:28:25,780 --> 00:28:29,540
 Ja sjećam sema da sam pokušavao

894
00:28:29,540 --> 00:28:32,180
 upisati se barem u Mostar na fakultet.

895
00:28:32,740 --> 00:28:34,340
 Eto, zna da sam Mostar iđo u fratre,

896
00:28:34,340 --> 00:28:34,780
 pa ono,

897
00:28:34,780 --> 00:28:36,460
 pa ću biti tu negdje blizu.

898
00:28:36,460 --> 00:28:39,660
 I nisu mi dali.

899
00:28:39,660 --> 00:28:40,840
 Ni braća, ni mater,

900
00:28:40,840 --> 00:28:42,580
 znači samo nećeš ti doli,

901
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,520
 ti ćeš od propastiti.

902
00:28:43,520 --> 00:28:44,300
 Ako pa vi ste doli,

903
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:45,040
 šta vama fali?

904
00:28:45,040 --> 00:28:46,980
 Ti moraš ići vama,

905
00:28:46,980 --> 00:28:47,920
 kad ti is pametan.

906
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:49,600
 Da, nemojte me na to.

907
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:51,260
 Moraš i gotovo.

908
00:28:51,260 --> 00:28:52,760
 Jedna sam moraš na državnu maturu,

909
00:28:52,760 --> 00:28:54,320
 koji će u fakultet,

910
00:28:54,320 --> 00:28:55,140
 i mi ćemo ti zabrati,

911
00:28:55,140 --> 00:28:56,500
 pa će se zabrati elektrotehniku.

912
00:28:56,500 --> 00:28:57,800
 Ne mogu u Zagreb,

913
00:28:57,860 --> 00:28:59,080
 gore su imao prebivalište,

914
00:28:59,080 --> 00:29:02,320
 koji svi imao svi negdje prebivalište,

915
00:29:02,320 --> 00:29:03,660
 pa tako je mene zapalo gore.

916
00:29:03,660 --> 00:29:05,240
 Tako je nam gore na fakultet,

917
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:06,100
 moram uspiliti.

918
00:29:06,100 --> 00:29:06,920
 Odem na fezb.

919
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:08,520
 I doli mi je super.

920
00:29:08,520 --> 00:29:09,020
 Da smo kolegi.

921
00:29:09,020 --> 00:29:10,440
 Više.

922
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:11,640
 Me je doli super bilo.

923
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:13,840
 Upadno sam finu ekipu.

924
00:29:13,840 --> 00:29:16,780
 Muna, Bruno, Josip,

925
00:29:16,780 --> 00:29:18,180
 svaki nas smo se družili,

926
00:29:18,180 --> 00:29:19,120
 učili smo zajedno.

927
00:29:19,120 --> 00:29:23,140
 Ali ja lina večer nisam mogu spavat.

928
00:29:23,140 --> 00:29:26,000
 Ja došao u dom,

929
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:26,760
 u sobu,

930
00:29:26,760 --> 00:29:27,760
 na večer umoran.

931
00:29:27,860 --> 00:29:28,640
 tamo, ne znam,

932
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:29,560
 20 dana i sati.

933
00:29:29,560 --> 00:29:30,480
 Samo da mi je zaspat.

934
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,340
 Nemogu ja oći,

935
00:29:31,340 --> 00:29:31,620
 bolam,

936
00:29:31,620 --> 00:29:32,520
 ko klikari,

937
00:29:32,520 --> 00:29:33,680
 nema šanse zaspat.

938
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:35,780
 I što?

939
00:29:35,780 --> 00:29:36,860
 U svoju ne mogu zaspat.

940
00:29:36,860 --> 00:29:37,980
 U glave samo,

941
00:29:37,980 --> 00:29:39,320
 aj, daj mi priliku,

942
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:40,180
 daj mi priliku.

943
00:29:40,180 --> 00:29:41,000
 Pa kako, bolam,

944
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:41,260
 daj,

945
00:29:41,260 --> 00:29:41,780
 sad priliku.

946
00:29:41,780 --> 00:29:42,560
 Eva došla do ovdje,

947
00:29:42,560 --> 00:29:43,840
 sam me gondio još opet nekje drugo.

948
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:44,100
 Da,

949
00:29:44,100 --> 00:29:45,380
 zeru me postoji.

950
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:47,080
 Ne znam iz da budem samo malo,

951
00:29:47,080 --> 00:29:47,760
 da budem migran.

952
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:48,420
 Ma jok.

953
00:29:48,420 --> 00:29:51,520
 22.11.

954
00:29:51,520 --> 00:29:54,320
 dolazim kući.

955
00:29:54,320 --> 00:29:55,320
 Znači,

956
00:29:57,860 --> 00:29:59,640
 od tamale iške prve kolokvije.

957
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:00,760
 I pokupio se.

958
00:30:00,760 --> 00:30:02,420
 Niko ništa ne zna,

959
00:30:02,420 --> 00:30:03,100
 osim fratra,

960
00:30:03,100 --> 00:30:04,140
 duhovnog asistenta.

961
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:05,180
 Ja mu kažem,

962
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:06,140
 ja bi u fratre,

963
00:30:06,140 --> 00:30:08,620
 on sam vam poslao poruku,

964
00:30:08,620 --> 00:30:09,300
 slava Isusu,

965
00:30:09,300 --> 00:30:10,040
 dođi kući,

966
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:10,640
 kad mog niješ,

967
00:30:10,640 --> 00:30:12,240
 pa ćemo reći tvoj ima.

968
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:12,780
 I to je sve.

969
00:30:12,780 --> 00:30:15,780
 Ja taj dan dolazim kući,

970
00:30:15,780 --> 00:30:21,100
 i mater teba voz babu u bolnicu,

971
00:30:21,100 --> 00:30:22,040
 negdje je žurla,

972
00:30:22,040 --> 00:30:23,880
 pa će sestresu po kući,

973
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:24,200
 pišu,

974
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:25,020
 da ću učeš šta.

975
00:30:25,020 --> 00:30:25,580
 Ja se pojavio,

976
00:30:25,580 --> 00:30:26,560
 u kući okle tebe,

977
00:30:27,420 --> 00:30:27,580
 rekao,

978
00:30:27,580 --> 00:30:28,900
 moram nešto za blagoslov kuće,

979
00:30:28,900 --> 00:30:30,000
 sađivati liste fratrima,

980
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,140
 šta ja znam vam od tamo,

981
00:30:31,140 --> 00:30:32,120
 vi smo nešto radili s ima,

982
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:32,460
 pa eto,

983
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:33,820
 tada sam to mogu reći,

984
00:30:33,820 --> 00:30:35,040
 da blagoslov je bio blizu.

985
00:30:35,040 --> 00:30:36,400
 Mater je kaže,

986
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:36,640
 dobro,

987
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,280
 ja odu u bolnicu,

988
00:30:37,280 --> 00:30:38,240
 pa vidit ćemo se kasnije.

989
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,600
 Ona je išla za moj stars babu.

990
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:42,660
 Međerime je taj fratr došao kod nas u kuću,

991
00:30:42,660 --> 00:30:45,160
 ali to je bilo prije toga samo jednom,

992
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:46,320
 kad je rekao,

993
00:30:46,320 --> 00:30:47,960
 za ovog glaća da ću onu fratre.

994
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:49,560
 Sad dolazi i ponovo,

995
00:30:50,280 --> 00:30:51,920
 braća sestre i ja u kući.

996
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:54,060
 Čača je bio u Njemačkoj na bavušteli.

997
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:55,800
 I šta je?

998
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:57,240
 Mora vam nešto reći,

999
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:57,860
 kaže fratr,

1000
00:30:57,860 --> 00:30:58,360
 ja ne mogu,

1001
00:30:58,360 --> 00:30:59,040
 ja se skamenio,

1002
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:00,000
 znači ne mogu,

1003
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:00,640
 ja ne postoji,

1004
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,580
 da mi je umor tada bilo,

1005
00:31:01,580 --> 00:31:02,220
 da rodio je pisalo,

1006
00:31:02,220 --> 00:31:02,800
 nema šanse.

1007
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:05,120
 I on kaže,

1008
00:31:05,120 --> 00:31:06,200
 braća vam u fratre.

1009
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:07,160
 I ovaj.

1010
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:09,600
 I oni se tu zanijemili,

1011
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:12,000
 braća su ušutila,

1012
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:14,160
 sestre su uplači,

1013
00:31:14,160 --> 00:31:14,980
 otišla u sobu.

1014
00:31:14,980 --> 00:31:17,840
 Nisu mogla ništa saći.

1015
00:31:17,840 --> 00:31:19,240
 Ova namađa sestra je bila mala,

1016
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:20,120
 nje je bilo koliko,

1017
00:31:20,120 --> 00:31:20,760
 pje, šest godina,

1018
00:31:20,760 --> 00:31:21,840
 nije ono ništa ni kontala,

1019
00:31:21,840 --> 00:31:23,780
 ali ove ostale već su znali.

1020
00:31:23,780 --> 00:31:25,240
 Šta to znači?

1021
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:27,600
 I mater sa braća,

1022
00:31:27,600 --> 00:31:28,600
 kasnije isma stara,

1023
00:31:28,600 --> 00:31:30,860
 vidi da smo svi mirni.

1024
00:31:30,860 --> 00:31:32,460
 To se nikad nije dogodilo,

1025
00:31:32,460 --> 00:31:33,140
 da sam je bil,

1026
00:31:33,140 --> 00:31:34,240
 kad smo u kući svi mirni,

1027
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:35,200
 da nije nije bilo tu.

1028
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,100
 Nikad.

1029
00:31:36,100 --> 00:31:37,220
 Tada i nikad više.

1030
00:31:37,220 --> 00:31:40,020
 O, sin, okledam tebe kući,

1031
00:31:40,020 --> 00:31:41,880
 aj, sidi pa ćete reći.

1032
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:43,220
 Ba, jedno sto puta,

1033
00:31:43,220 --> 00:31:43,960
 sidi pa ćete reći.

1034
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:45,080
 Pa, ne, treba se recimo,

1035
00:31:45,080 --> 00:31:46,160
 sidi pa ćete reći.

1036
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:47,480
 Nakon sto puta,

1037
00:31:47,480 --> 00:31:48,300
 zesila,

1038
00:31:48,300 --> 00:31:50,880
 i ja kada,

1039
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:51,960
 maja koja biu u fratre.

1040
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:54,520
 Dajmo optelona,

1041
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:55,380
 uzela mu optel,

1042
00:31:55,380 --> 00:31:56,040
 zove Čaču.

1043
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:56,720
 Ostan telefon,

1044
00:31:56,720 --> 00:31:57,980
 i ona imela mu optela tada,

1045
00:31:57,980 --> 00:31:59,720
 zoveu Čaču u Njemačku.

1046
00:31:59,720 --> 00:32:00,980
 I kažem,

1047
00:32:00,980 --> 00:32:02,000
 evo i ovaj poludio.

1048
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,140
 Šta je sad?

1049
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:04,160
 oče i ovaj u fratre.

1050
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:06,440
 Poklopi slušalca.

1051
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:07,720
 Zovem telefon ponovno.

1052
00:32:07,720 --> 00:32:08,260
 Čača zove,

1053
00:32:08,260 --> 00:32:09,080
 daj mi na telefon.

1054
00:32:09,080 --> 00:32:09,920
 Ja se javi.

1055
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:11,340
 Ti si lud,

1056
00:32:11,340 --> 00:32:12,180
 fali li ti para?

1057
00:32:12,180 --> 00:32:12,880
 Elovo, Elovo.

1058
00:32:12,880 --> 00:32:14,240
 Da te to, sto pitanja.

1059
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:16,500
 Onda na kraju samo,

1060
00:32:16,500 --> 00:32:17,840
 aj, završ fakultet,

1061
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:18,760
 pa onda u fratre.

1062
00:32:18,760 --> 00:32:19,860
 Ja, ne mogu.

1063
00:32:19,860 --> 00:32:20,740
 Ona ima šanse.

1064
00:32:20,740 --> 00:32:21,880
 Ja sad moram,

1065
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:22,320
 ja ću imat,

1066
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:22,980
 ako sad ne vodem.

1067
00:32:22,980 --> 00:32:24,260
 Moram otit' sada.

1068
00:32:24,260 --> 00:32:26,780
 I ništa.

1069
00:32:26,780 --> 00:32:28,140
 Poklopi se slušalca.

1070
00:32:28,140 --> 00:32:29,780
 Ti si lud.

1071
00:32:31,120 --> 00:32:32,440
 ja odem na fakultet,

1072
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,840
 izbrišan sa fakulteta,

1073
00:32:33,840 --> 00:32:36,500
 ima odem razgova s provincijalom,

1074
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:37,320
 ome primi,

1075
00:32:37,320 --> 00:32:38,620
 odem u fratre.

1076
00:32:39,580 --> 00:32:40,060
 Sjećam se,

1077
00:32:40,060 --> 00:32:41,340
 ušao sam u samostan,

1078
00:32:41,340 --> 00:32:44,040
 bilo je 28. večer.

1079
00:32:44,040 --> 00:32:50,040
 To je bio prvi dan došašća.

1080
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:53,220
 Ja lega spavat u večer,

1081
00:32:53,220 --> 00:32:55,240
 ja sam sviđao kodam sam kući došao,

1082
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:57,140
 napokon kodam sam kući došao.

1083
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,320
 Rekao sam Bogu,

1084
00:32:58,320 --> 00:33:00,340
 imaš samo jedan dan,

1085
00:33:00,340 --> 00:33:02,040
 bilo kodam se meni samostan svidio,

1086
00:33:02,040 --> 00:33:03,240
 ali nisam znao šta je samostan.

1087
00:33:03,280 --> 00:33:04,400
 nisam znao šta je posao samostan,

1088
00:33:04,400 --> 00:33:06,500
 ne u Širokom ni u Mostaru ni u Dunu ni šta,

1089
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:07,800
 u Vazdavu posuću bio,

1090
00:33:07,800 --> 00:33:09,100
 sam nigdje nišao.

1091
00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:11,360
 Tako da sam mi rekao,

1092
00:33:11,360 --> 00:33:13,100
 imaš jedan dan da mi se sve svidi.

1093
00:33:13,100 --> 00:33:14,080
 Mi se ne svidi,

1094
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:14,900
 ali do drugi dan.

1095
00:33:14,900 --> 00:33:16,440
 Ali mi je sve svidilo.

1096
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:17,460
 I sad,

1097
00:33:17,460 --> 00:33:18,920
 i jaš uvijek osjećam miris,

1098
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:21,440
 kad sam tek prvi podošao samostan,

1099
00:33:21,440 --> 00:33:22,180
 ošao osjećam miris,

1100
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:22,900
 posla Ture,

1101
00:33:23,580 --> 00:33:26,260
 nije to bila večera.

1102
00:33:26,260 --> 00:33:27,480
 Ja sam ušao samostan,

1103
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:28,220
 prazan samostan.

1104
00:33:28,220 --> 00:33:28,820
 Mi su svi bili,

1105
00:33:28,820 --> 00:33:29,100
 ne znam,

1106
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:30,080
 na probama za Široki,

1107
00:33:30,080 --> 00:33:32,000
 pošto je dan 29.

1108
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:33,720
 sa skupima svi fratikom na brijegu,

1109
00:33:33,720 --> 00:33:35,580
 pa niko nije bio samostan.

1110
00:33:35,580 --> 00:33:36,860
 Došao do prazan samostan.

1111
00:33:36,860 --> 00:33:38,100
 Niko me nije dočekao.

1112
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:40,540
 Tako je to bilo isto malo meni,

1113
00:33:40,540 --> 00:33:41,960
 čudno,

1114
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:43,660
 ako on tam tako valja treba biti.

1115
00:33:43,660 --> 00:33:44,560
 Niti znam di mi je sova,

1116
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:45,180
 ne znam di mi je mišla,

1117
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:45,760
 bezalutam,

1118
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:47,060
 pa samostan ako neko ne dođe.

1119
00:33:47,060 --> 00:33:48,060
 Tako da,

1120
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:50,440
 to je neki prvi korad samostan

1121
00:33:50,440 --> 00:33:51,320
 da se bili takvi.

1122
00:33:51,320 --> 00:33:53,600
 Bilo je tu možda još neki stvari,

1123
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:57,420
 ali ja vidit ću možda kasnije budeo.

1124
00:33:57,420 --> 00:33:57,880
 Ajde.

1125
00:33:57,880 --> 00:33:58,800
 Pa evo,

1126
00:33:58,800 --> 00:33:59,880
 koji možeš nešto reći?

1127
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:02,660
 Bilo je stvari koje su uticale

1128
00:34:02,660 --> 00:34:03,680
 na ovo sve,

1129
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:04,720
 ne izravno.

1130
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:07,380
 Dakle, da ja postanem fratak,

1131
00:34:07,380 --> 00:34:08,800
 to ne.

1132
00:34:08,800 --> 00:34:11,740
 Ali uticale da ja malo drugačije

1133
00:34:11,740 --> 00:34:13,040
 razmišljam o životu.

1134
00:34:13,040 --> 00:34:15,020
 Definitivno.

1135
00:34:15,020 --> 00:34:16,980
 O tome da će život nekad završiti.

1136
00:34:16,980 --> 00:34:19,940
 To je definitivno.

1137
00:34:20,080 --> 00:34:21,360
 tako,

1138
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:24,200
 mislim da sam se bili ovo govorila,

1139
00:34:24,200 --> 00:34:25,480
 sam im došlo da kažem,

1140
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:26,220
 a to je očito ono,

1141
00:34:26,220 --> 00:34:27,720
 tako kad sam Bogu rekao,

1142
00:34:27,720 --> 00:34:28,400
 ako je teško,

1143
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:30,180
 mena moram recimo da kažem.

1144
00:34:30,180 --> 00:34:32,360
 Ovo moje ukući ne znaju.

1145
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:34,340
 Ovo ovo meni znaju.

1146
00:34:34,340 --> 00:34:35,280
 Čivao me ekskluzivu,

1147
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:35,940
 dravi gledate.

1148
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:37,820
 Sada je ekskluziva,

1149
00:34:37,820 --> 00:34:38,260
 nije li,

1150
00:34:38,260 --> 00:34:40,060
 neka velika priča,

1151
00:34:40,060 --> 00:34:40,500
 nije li to,

1152
00:34:40,500 --> 00:34:40,980
 ne znam,

1153
00:34:40,980 --> 00:34:41,480
 ali ovo,

1154
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:43,340
 malo ljudi o meni zna.

1155
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:46,680
 Da je se ta stvar dogodila

1156
00:34:46,680 --> 00:34:47,320
 i želam još,

1157
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:48,800
 oče moji saznat na ovakav nač

1158
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,880
 na kovo budu gledali,

1159
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:50,940
 nadam se da neće.

1160
00:34:50,940 --> 00:34:51,920
 Mama, tata,

1161
00:34:51,920 --> 00:34:52,860
 ne mojete se ljudi.

1162
00:34:52,860 --> 00:34:56,340
 Dakle,

1163
00:34:56,340 --> 00:34:57,480
 tada

1164
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:59,080
 sam bio

1165
00:34:59,080 --> 00:35:01,300
 treći i srednje.

1166
00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:03,100
 Znam to,

1167
00:35:03,100 --> 00:35:04,240
 jer bratiš na ekskluziju.

1168
00:35:04,240 --> 00:35:05,240
 Dakle,

1169
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:06,600
 početak trećeg i srednje je bio.

1170
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:08,580
 sjećam se,

1171
00:35:08,580 --> 00:35:10,660
 taj danas došli neki gosti u kuću.

1172
00:35:10,660 --> 00:35:13,180
 Ja sam nešto nisam osjećao dobro,

1173
00:35:13,180 --> 00:35:15,560
 kažem mami da nisam dobro,

1174
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:16,260
 samo otiću,

1175
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:17,360
 kažem ti u sobu,

1176
00:35:17,360 --> 00:35:19,880
 što je otošao u sobu

1177
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:20,660
 i ponio sa sobom to,

1178
00:35:20,660 --> 00:35:20,900
 oprimjer,

1179
00:35:20,900 --> 00:35:22,460
 izmirim temperaturu.

1180
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:24,780
 ovaj.

1181
00:35:24,780 --> 00:35:28,640
 A inače,

1182
00:35:28,640 --> 00:35:29,960
 mi nikad nije hladno u životu.

1183
00:35:29,960 --> 00:35:31,080
 Tada,

1184
00:35:31,080 --> 00:35:32,840
 nam je bilo četiri deke

1185
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:33,640
 i tri organa.

1186
00:35:33,640 --> 00:35:35,460
 Ja se tresim ovako,

1187
00:35:35,460 --> 00:35:36,700
 sklakućem od kauča.

1188
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:38,680
 Koliko je meni hladno bila.

1189
00:35:38,680 --> 00:35:40,340
 Mjerim temperaturu,

1190
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:42,780
 toplomjer pukao pod rukom.

1191
00:35:42,780 --> 00:35:43,640
 Ona je živim bio.

1192
00:35:43,640 --> 00:35:45,340
 Pukao je,

1193
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:46,800
 od kolika je temperatura bila.

1194
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:48,660
 od okolje je to pome,

1195
00:35:48,660 --> 00:35:49,700
 koliko je smoga ima.

1196
00:35:49,700 --> 00:35:51,120
 Mislim, 45 ovom mjeri.

1197
00:35:51,120 --> 00:35:51,600
 Mislim, sve bro.

1198
00:35:51,600 --> 00:35:54,080
 Nije važno to,

1199
00:35:54,080 --> 00:35:55,720
 ono što se dogodilo posle toga,

1200
00:35:55,720 --> 00:35:58,620
 što moji nikad nisu saznali.

1201
00:35:58,620 --> 00:36:02,680
 Ovo će čudno zvučat.

1202
00:36:02,680 --> 00:36:04,100
 Ja sam tada umro.

1203
00:36:04,100 --> 00:36:07,060
 Ja živio sam iskustvo kliničke smrti.

1204
00:36:07,060 --> 00:36:11,920
 To je bilo su noć.

1205
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:15,000
 Mislim, ja sam tek jutri se vratio.

1206
00:36:16,140 --> 00:36:17,380
 Među vremenu

1207
00:36:17,380 --> 00:36:20,880
 sam susreo tada pokolnju rodicu Lidiju,

1208
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:23,640
 pokolnju tetku na jedu

1209
00:36:23,640 --> 00:36:27,120
 i razgovarao sam s gazdom.

1210
00:36:27,120 --> 00:36:29,140
 Što bi se rekla?

1211
00:36:29,140 --> 00:36:29,800
 S Isusom.

1212
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:32,320
 O detaljima razgovar je tome,

1213
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,060
 to me ne bi.

1214
00:36:33,060 --> 00:36:35,540
 Ali da je to celo na mene

1215
00:36:35,540 --> 00:36:37,740
 da razmišljam drugačije o životu

1216
00:36:37,740 --> 00:36:40,320
 i da se bilo kad mora završiti.

1217
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:42,740
 Da ne mora to biti

1218
00:36:42,740 --> 00:36:44,200
 ni starost, ni bolest,

1219
00:36:44,200 --> 00:36:45,160
 ni nesreća.

1220
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:46,920
 pokoje je dovoljno samo.

1221
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:48,240
 Ja sam gotov.

1222
00:36:48,240 --> 00:36:51,200
 Ovdje ga treba biti spreman.

1223
00:36:51,200 --> 00:36:53,660
 I to me je potaklo

1224
00:36:53,660 --> 00:36:55,260
 da mijenjam neke stvari u sebi

1225
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:57,200
 koje možda dogodano da nisam mogo promijeniti.

1226
00:36:57,860 --> 00:37:00,400
 ali to je iskustvo mene je promijenilo

1227
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:03,360
 iako nije, kažem, bilo odlučujući da postanem fratar.

1228
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:05,860
 Bilo odlučujući da postanem vjernik.

1229
00:37:08,240 --> 00:37:10,500
 Tako da vjerujem da je u korijen

1230
00:37:10,500 --> 00:37:12,340
 opet svega toga opet i ovo iskustvo

1231
00:37:12,340 --> 00:37:14,360
 bilo, iako mi ja zbog toga

1232
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:16,700
 ne osjećam obaveza da sam ja morao tići u fratar.

1233
00:37:16,700 --> 00:37:18,360
 To je poprlo drugačiji poziv.

1234
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:20,940
 Ovo je možda bilo početak obraćanja

1235
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:21,960
 da se tako izrazim.

1236
00:37:21,960 --> 00:37:23,140
 Ja ko sam bio uvijek vjernik,

1237
00:37:23,140 --> 00:37:24,640
 ali uvijek ono,

1238
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:26,860
 ko svi ostali, na papiru si tu,

1239
00:37:26,860 --> 00:37:28,340
 ono uvijek se rodovice namisi,

1240
00:37:28,500 --> 00:37:30,360
 ali nešto doživljivaš toliko duboko,

1241
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,080
 možda i ne.

1242
00:37:31,080 --> 00:37:34,360
 Ono, osim onoga što moraš slavit, slaviš,

1243
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:35,680
 ostale da mi nešto zanima,

1244
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:37,680
 šta crkva govori, boli me briga.

1245
00:37:37,680 --> 00:37:39,680
 Ali nakon tog iskustva

1246
00:37:39,680 --> 00:37:43,740
 su se stvari u meni bitno promijenile.

1247
00:37:43,740 --> 00:37:44,860
 I moj način molitve,

1248
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:45,720
 i jednost sa zbogom,

1249
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:46,520
 i prema drugima,

1250
00:37:46,520 --> 00:37:48,640
 i se bitno promijenilo.

1251
00:37:48,640 --> 00:37:50,920
 Cijela perspektiva, cijeli život notenje.

1252
00:37:50,920 --> 00:37:51,660
 Absolutno.

1253
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:55,340
 Sve, sve, mislim, ovo me sam morao dugo,

1254
00:37:55,340 --> 00:37:56,660
 ali da ne krademo vrijeme

1255
00:37:56,660 --> 00:37:58,420
 za druge stvari, nećemo.

1256
00:37:58,500 --> 00:37:59,180
 Pa evo, nisam,

1257
00:37:59,180 --> 00:38:00,540
 inako ti imaš još nešto reći,

1258
00:38:00,540 --> 00:38:01,020
 nastavio.

1259
00:38:01,020 --> 00:38:03,800
 Zašao se i intrigantne stvari.

1260
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:05,980
 Ostat ćemo na tome.

1261
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:08,040
 Dobro, neka nešto ostane između vas.

1262
00:38:08,040 --> 00:38:10,980
 Evo, govoreći općenito o poziv,

1263
00:38:10,980 --> 00:38:12,940
 kako uopće razlušiti poziv,

1264
00:38:12,940 --> 00:38:14,200
 kako znati da nas,

1265
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:16,320
 Bog, što Bog želi za nas.

1266
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:18,100
 Evo, ne mora samo srati nužno

1267
00:38:18,100 --> 00:38:19,540
 o duhovnom pozivu,

1268
00:38:19,540 --> 00:38:21,360
 nego evo, brašnom pozivu.

1269
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:23,700
 U drugom, sve u životu može biti poziv.

1270
00:38:23,700 --> 00:38:26,680
 Ja vjerujem da zato ne postoje

1271
00:38:26,680 --> 00:38:28,500
 neka definicija, neko objašenje

1272
00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:30,200
 da ja mogu tebi reći.

1273
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:32,300
 Kad doživiš to, to, to i to, to ti je to.

1274
00:38:32,300 --> 00:38:34,340
 Kad doživiš to i to, to je poziv na ovo.

1275
00:38:34,340 --> 00:38:37,100
 Bog svima govori na različite načine,

1276
00:38:37,100 --> 00:38:38,480
 ali uvijek je to način

1277
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:40,160
 na koji to ta osoba mora skontati.

1278
00:38:41,460 --> 00:38:43,080
 Meni je to moje nespavanje bilo znak

1279
00:38:43,080 --> 00:38:44,080
 da vam otići u fratre.

1280
00:38:44,080 --> 00:38:46,100
 To je možda mom cimeno bilo,

1281
00:38:46,100 --> 00:38:47,820
 Bože, ovome treba biti za spavanje.

1282
00:38:47,820 --> 00:38:49,120
 Ovo nije dobar u glavu.

1283
00:38:49,120 --> 00:38:51,380
 A meni je bilo da trebamo otići u fratre.

1284
00:38:51,380 --> 00:38:53,340
 Nekom je drugom će našto drugo biti znak,

1285
00:38:53,340 --> 00:38:55,480
 da oženi baš tu ženo,

1286
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:56,340
 ne neku drugu.

1287
00:38:56,340 --> 00:38:58,200
 Ili ne znam, da ostane,

1288
00:38:58,200 --> 00:39:01,520
 da živi sve to u samoći.

1289
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:03,140
 Što Pavo izriče

1290
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:05,480
 kao najveći način žrtve.

1291
00:39:05,960 --> 00:39:08,880
 Da se čovjek ne ženi je najbolje za njega.

1292
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:10,660
 Ko se oženi ne čini grijeh,

1293
00:39:10,660 --> 00:39:11,700
 ali bolje je da se ne ženi.

1294
00:39:11,700 --> 00:39:13,500
 A danas da neko ostane nožen,

1295
00:39:13,500 --> 00:39:15,560
 rekli bi da nije baš dobar u glavu.

1296
00:39:15,560 --> 00:39:18,980
 Tako da vjerujem da Bog jasno

1297
00:39:18,980 --> 00:39:20,580
 svakom srcu govore na način

1298
00:39:20,580 --> 00:39:21,760
 na koji ono mora skontati.

1299
00:39:21,760 --> 00:39:23,760
 Niko drugi ne mora moći skontati.

1300
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:25,680
 A toj osobi, to bode oči,

1301
00:39:25,680 --> 00:39:28,660
 bode srce, jednostavno izgaraš od čežnje,

1302
00:39:28,660 --> 00:39:30,280
 da tu stvar ispuniš.

1303
00:39:30,280 --> 00:39:32,460
 Možda to nije stvara koja se sviđa,

1304
00:39:32,460 --> 00:39:34,840
 pa to pokušavaš odkloniti od sebe

1305
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:37,040
 i upravda to nečim drugim.

1306
00:39:37,040 --> 00:39:39,160
 O, to me džaba, baca ovakve misle.

1307
00:39:39,160 --> 00:39:40,440
 To je samo neka moja želja

1308
00:39:40,440 --> 00:39:41,620
 koju ja zapravo ne želim.

1309
00:39:41,620 --> 00:39:45,680
 Zato što bježimo zbog strahova,

1310
00:39:45,680 --> 00:39:48,020
 nedostojnosti, ne znam,

1311
00:39:48,020 --> 00:39:49,640
 slabosti, nesavršenost,

1312
00:39:49,640 --> 00:39:50,340
 čega god očiš,

1313
00:39:50,340 --> 00:39:53,460
 onda te Boži poziv i bjegavaš.

1314
00:39:53,460 --> 00:39:54,460
 Nekaj to opet očekaj.

1315
00:39:54,460 --> 00:39:55,760
 Evo i ja sam bježao na neki način.

1316
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:56,640
 A ne možeš pobići.

1317
00:39:56,640 --> 00:39:57,880
 Opet me dočekalo džaba.

1318
00:39:57,880 --> 00:40:00,880
 Evo, spomenuo si i svoj roditelj,

1319
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:02,480
 njihovo teško, prihvaćanjem.

1320
00:40:02,640 --> 00:40:05,180
 To je sve neka vrsta kriza,

1321
00:40:05,180 --> 00:40:08,060
 kušnji koje dolaze tijeku poziva.

1322
00:40:08,060 --> 00:40:11,340
 Vjeruju još mi da meni to nisu bile kušnje.

1323
00:40:11,340 --> 00:40:12,780
 Meni je to pomoglo.

1324
00:40:12,780 --> 00:40:15,440
 Meni je pomoglo da se ja

1325
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:17,080
 od svoje obitelje,

1326
00:40:17,080 --> 00:40:18,380
 ovo će sad zvuča grubo,

1327
00:40:18,380 --> 00:40:20,480
 oprostite moji ukćani,

1328
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:22,440
 zvuča će grubo,

1329
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:24,000
 ali što je isto rekao u evanđelju,

1330
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:25,800
 pusti da mrtve pokapaju mrtve.

1331
00:40:26,180 --> 00:40:28,220
 Svaki koji se okrene kad uzme pluk,

1332
00:40:28,220 --> 00:40:29,300
 nije dostan mene.

1333
00:40:29,300 --> 00:40:31,340
 Jednostavno,

1334
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:34,340
 taj se neki prekid u odnosu,

1335
00:40:34,340 --> 00:40:35,920
 u smislu neke navjezanosti,

1336
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:36,760
 mora dogoditi.

1337
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:40,760
 Meni je to pomoglo da se ja od njih udalim na neki način.

1338
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:42,780
 Ja njih danas volim jako puno,

1339
00:40:42,780 --> 00:40:43,620
 da će to me daža čelja,

1340
00:40:43,620 --> 00:40:44,840
 na svijetu su mi moja kućna čelja,

1341
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:45,860
 braća, srdećača i mater.

1342
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,320
 Bez njih ne bi bilo mene.

1343
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:50,400
 Da im triba krvi sa bi da,

1344
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,780
 da meni triba on bi mi da,

1345
00:40:51,780 --> 00:40:52,780
 ja sam mu to uvjeren.

1346
00:40:52,780 --> 00:40:54,980
 Znaš, se odnosi duboko promijelno

1347
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:56,220
 nakon svega što je bilo.

1348
00:40:56,220 --> 00:40:59,820
 Ali meni je pomoglo da ne mislim toliko

1349
00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:00,620
 ni o kući,

1350
00:41:00,620 --> 00:41:02,300
 ni o nekim drugim stvarima,

1351
00:41:02,300 --> 00:41:04,440
 da ne osjećam neku nostalgiju,

1352
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:05,160
 reću tako,

1353
00:41:05,160 --> 00:41:07,800
 nego da što prije prihvatim samostan

1354
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:08,520
 kao svoj dom.

1355
00:41:08,520 --> 00:41:10,800
 Sjećam se kad sam prije poljošao kući,

1356
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:13,320
 odnosno uposrevatio se do svojih,

1357
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:14,320
 ono za praznike,

1358
00:41:15,220 --> 00:41:16,940
 govori joo, sad moram kući u mostaru.

1359
00:41:16,940 --> 00:41:18,660
 A sina, pa ti sveć kući?

1360
00:41:18,660 --> 00:41:21,260
 A je go, majko, moja je kuća sad u mostaru.

1361
00:41:21,260 --> 00:41:23,980
 I to, nju je to pogledalo

1362
00:41:23,980 --> 00:41:24,740
 to kad se sićam.

1363
00:41:24,740 --> 00:41:25,720
 Rekao, majko, prosti,

1364
00:41:25,720 --> 00:41:27,720
 ali sa stvari tako stoje.

1365
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:29,400
 Meni je kuća je ovde,

1366
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:30,400
 ali tamo gdje živim,

1367
00:41:30,400 --> 00:41:31,800
 to mi je više kuća.

1368
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:32,700
 Vama hvala na svemu,

1369
00:41:32,700 --> 00:41:34,240
 ali ja sam sad vratar.

1370
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:36,740
 Tako da, to mi je pomoglo.

1371
00:41:36,740 --> 00:41:38,200
 Bilo je možda malo bolno,

1372
00:41:38,200 --> 00:41:40,680
 ali pomoglo da se brže prebacim

1373
00:41:40,680 --> 00:41:41,740
 tamo i se vam prebacim.

1374
00:41:41,740 --> 00:41:44,080
 Evo kako se nositi s nekim drugim kućima

1375
00:41:45,220 --> 00:41:47,220
 možda pitanje dostojnosti

1376
00:41:47,220 --> 00:41:49,440
 i ostala pitanja

1377
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:50,940
 koja sami po sebi nameću?

1378
00:41:50,940 --> 00:41:52,900
 Bilo je drugi kućnje,

1379
00:41:52,900 --> 00:41:54,600
 ja neću reći da nije samo ovo,

1380
00:41:54,600 --> 00:41:55,600
 ovo nije bila kućnja,

1381
00:41:55,600 --> 00:41:56,900
 ali drugi stvari, pogotovo...

1382
00:41:56,900 --> 00:41:57,760
 Ovo tebi nije konkretno,

1383
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:58,300
 nekom drugom možda je.

1384
00:41:58,300 --> 00:41:59,640
 Nekom drugom vjerojatno je, da.

1385
00:41:59,640 --> 00:42:02,280
 Nedostojnost,

1386
00:42:02,280 --> 00:42:04,640
 tam danas me to obala muči.

1387
00:42:04,640 --> 00:42:07,640
 Iako ja i vjerujem i znam

1388
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:10,260
 da nikad neću moći biti dostojan,

1389
00:42:10,260 --> 00:42:12,380
 da ne mogu sebe učiniti

1390
00:42:12,380 --> 00:42:13,740
 dostao ni na koji način,

1391
00:42:14,120 --> 00:42:15,520
 ni ti ovo zasluga moja

1392
00:42:15,520 --> 00:42:16,320
 ni bila čija,

1393
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:18,200
 nego je Boži dar.

1394
00:42:18,200 --> 00:42:21,820
 Bog dane milost da postanem nešto,

1395
00:42:21,820 --> 00:42:23,200
 zašto ja nemam

1396
00:42:23,200 --> 00:42:25,160
 nećeo isposobnosti,

1397
00:42:25,160 --> 00:42:26,360
 nego nema mogućnosti

1398
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:27,420
 bez njegove milosti.

1399
00:42:27,420 --> 00:42:28,820
 Sakrament su njegova milost,

1400
00:42:28,820 --> 00:42:29,920
 pa posakramenturira sam

1401
00:42:29,920 --> 00:42:30,780
 postao svećenik.

1402
00:42:30,780 --> 00:42:33,680
 Ne mogu nikad sebe učiniti dostao.

1403
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:34,800
 Ima lome, činji dostao.

1404
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:37,060
 Ne da on će na meni učiniti

1405
00:42:37,060 --> 00:42:38,220
 neki čarobni čin,

1406
00:42:38,220 --> 00:42:39,700
 pa da postanem bezgrešan.

1407
00:42:40,700 --> 00:42:43,040
 nego time što je Isu zamenio na križu umro,

1408
00:42:43,040 --> 00:42:44,420
 to je meni učinilo dostojanim

1409
00:42:44,420 --> 00:42:46,100
 svega što mi Bogu želi dati.

1410
00:42:46,100 --> 00:42:47,320
 I raja, pa dalje.

1411
00:42:47,320 --> 00:42:51,020
 Nikakva druga tu zasluga ne postoji.

1412
00:42:51,620 --> 00:42:55,060
 Tako da, što se tiče te kušnjene nedostojnosti,

1413
00:42:55,060 --> 00:42:57,200
 može samo ići istinom

1414
00:42:57,200 --> 00:42:58,200
 protiv toga.

1415
00:42:58,200 --> 00:43:00,440
 Jesam, nedostojan sam,

1416
00:43:00,440 --> 00:43:01,760
 ne vridim toliko,

1417
00:43:01,760 --> 00:43:03,440
 prav sam i pepeo, prašna,

1418
00:43:03,440 --> 00:43:04,160
 obična gnjila,

1419
00:43:04,160 --> 00:43:05,300
 ništa ne vridim, bjeda.

1420
00:43:05,300 --> 00:43:08,140
 Ali Bog me čini većim od toga.

1421
00:43:08,140 --> 00:43:09,700
 Ne jer sam ga tražao,

1422
00:43:09,700 --> 00:43:10,820
 ne jer sam ga pitao,

1423
00:43:10,820 --> 00:43:12,240
 nego jer njemu to triba.

1424
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:13,760
 Zašto? Ja ne znam.

1425
00:43:14,080 --> 00:43:15,640
 Mogu joj stopu bolje proći s nekim drugim.

1426
00:43:15,640 --> 00:43:16,060
 Stopom.

1427
00:43:16,060 --> 00:43:18,640
 Ali jok, ti je ovako.

1428
00:43:18,640 --> 00:43:20,060
 Zašto to pitaći ovako

1429
00:43:20,060 --> 00:43:20,820
 kad dođe je na pegori?

1430
00:43:20,820 --> 00:43:22,060
 Ako dođe?

1431
00:43:22,060 --> 00:43:23,800
 Kako i Franjo govori,

1432
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:25,860
 tko si ti je o predsatki Bože moja,

1433
00:43:25,860 --> 00:43:28,420
 tko sam ja nekorisni sluga tvoja.

1434
00:43:28,420 --> 00:43:29,520
 To ti je to.

1435
00:43:29,520 --> 00:43:30,720
 Najgorije od sve djece,

1436
00:43:30,720 --> 00:43:31,720
 evo me taj sam ti.

1437
00:43:31,720 --> 00:43:34,840
 A evo kako izgleda ta vaša Franjevačka,

1438
00:43:34,840 --> 00:43:37,820
 to je, jesi ti prvo redovnik ili svećenik?

1439
00:43:37,820 --> 00:43:39,400
 Prvo sam redovnik,

1440
00:43:39,400 --> 00:43:40,720
 tek onda svećenik.

1441
00:43:40,720 --> 00:43:43,380
 Dakle sam postao, najprije sam postao fratar,

1442
00:43:44,080 --> 00:43:45,840
 da bi postao svećenik.

1443
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:48,580
 Najprije sam položio zavete,

1444
00:43:48,580 --> 00:43:51,740
 pa sam onda primio se kramenac svetog reda

1445
00:43:51,740 --> 00:43:53,280
 zakonovata pa svećeništva.

1446
00:43:53,280 --> 00:43:56,480
 Mislim, imao slučaje koji su već bili svećenici,

1447
00:43:56,480 --> 00:43:57,340
 pa postali Franjevačka.

1448
00:43:57,340 --> 00:43:58,260
 Bilo je i toga.

1449
00:43:58,260 --> 00:43:59,000
 Bilo je i toga.

1450
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:00,100
 Nedavno baš konos u provinciji

1451
00:44:00,100 --> 00:44:01,100
 odošao jedan što je bio

1452
00:44:01,100 --> 00:44:02,320
 predskojena na biskupiji,

1453
00:44:02,320 --> 00:44:03,280
 pa je prešao kod nas

1454
00:44:03,280 --> 00:44:04,440
 i postao je Franjevačka.

1455
00:44:04,440 --> 00:44:06,020
 Tako da imaju takvih slučajeva.

1456
00:44:06,020 --> 00:44:09,660
 Ali ja vjerujem da pa je podostojanstvo

1457
00:44:09,660 --> 00:44:10,920
 išlo najprije da sam svećenik,

1458
00:44:11,020 --> 00:44:11,940
 onda Franjevac.

1459
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:14,400
 Sam Franjevac je govorio

1460
00:44:14,400 --> 00:44:15,420
 kad vidim pred sobom

1461
00:44:15,420 --> 00:44:16,500
 Anđela i svećenika,

1462
00:44:16,500 --> 00:44:17,840
 poklonit ću se svećeniku.

1463
00:44:17,840 --> 00:44:19,700
 Tako da je vjerujem da je veće do stranstva

1464
00:44:19,700 --> 00:44:20,380
 to što sam svećenik,

1465
00:44:20,380 --> 00:44:21,120
 što sam fratar,

1466
00:44:21,120 --> 00:44:22,980
 ali u nas učilo smo redomnici

1467
00:44:22,980 --> 00:44:24,700
 i svećenic, pa ono tako nema.

1468
00:44:24,700 --> 00:44:26,420
 A kako ide ta vaša formacija

1469
00:44:26,420 --> 00:44:28,360
 Franjevačka i svećenička?

1470
00:44:28,360 --> 00:44:31,640
 Najprije imaš postulaturu,

1471
00:44:31,640 --> 00:44:32,860
 na Mostaru.

1472
00:44:32,860 --> 00:44:33,720
 Ja sam dole bio,

1473
00:44:33,720 --> 00:44:36,460
 dakle, od 28. danestoga

1474
00:44:36,460 --> 00:44:38,220
 do 14. i sedmoga.

1475
00:44:38,220 --> 00:44:41,880
 Onda smo 15. imali oblačenje u posušju,

1476
00:44:41,880 --> 00:44:45,680
 jedna smišljena u novcijat na humac.

1477
00:44:45,680 --> 00:44:48,360
 To traje skoro godine dana,

1478
00:44:48,360 --> 00:44:50,740
 tijan dana kraće od godine dana.

1479
00:44:50,740 --> 00:44:53,420
 Priprema za prve zavijete,

1480
00:44:53,420 --> 00:44:54,160
 privremene,

1481
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:55,260
 poslušnosti,

1482
00:44:55,260 --> 00:44:56,580
 siromaštvo i čistoće,

1483
00:44:56,700 --> 00:44:57,780
 život, kušnje,

1484
00:44:57,780 --> 00:45:00,180
 odvojenosti od svojih,

1485
00:45:00,180 --> 00:45:00,620
 od, ne znam,

1486
00:45:00,620 --> 00:45:01,680
 od interneta,

1487
00:45:01,680 --> 00:45:02,840
 ograničenih se nekih,

1488
00:45:02,840 --> 00:45:03,100
 ne znam,

1489
00:45:03,100 --> 00:45:03,940
 i ja stvarima.

1490
00:45:03,940 --> 00:45:05,560
 Mi se vježbaš ti tražiš,

1491
00:45:05,560 --> 00:45:06,660
 to od zajednice što ti treba.

1492
00:45:06,660 --> 00:45:07,520
 Kad je za teba nešto

1493
00:45:07,520 --> 00:45:08,680
 te baš pokučat meštru,

1494
00:45:08,680 --> 00:45:09,820
 meštru treba me to i to,

1495
00:45:09,820 --> 00:45:10,800
 mogu li, ne mogu li,

1496
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:11,360
 vamo tamo,

1497
00:45:11,360 --> 00:45:12,140
 nemaš čaparca,

1498
00:45:12,140 --> 00:45:12,820
 nemaš ništa,

1499
00:45:12,820 --> 00:45:14,300
 nemaš otići sam

1500
00:45:14,300 --> 00:45:15,240
 kad hoćeš ili hoćeš,

1501
00:45:15,240 --> 00:45:16,900
 nego imaš pravo ići

1502
00:45:16,900 --> 00:45:18,100
 kad, ono,

1503
00:45:18,180 --> 00:45:18,980
 neku određenu trenutu

1504
00:45:18,980 --> 00:45:19,820
 smo određena mjesta,

1505
00:45:19,820 --> 00:45:21,200
 to je prošetat,

1506
00:45:21,200 --> 00:45:22,180
 ono, ispred samostana,

1507
00:45:22,180 --> 00:45:23,240
 takve neke stvari,

1508
00:45:23,240 --> 00:45:24,400
 ali, ono,

1509
00:45:24,400 --> 00:45:24,900
 otići, ne znam,

1510
00:45:24,900 --> 00:45:25,400
 u trgovinu,

1511
00:45:25,400 --> 00:45:26,040
 kad nešto treba,

1512
00:45:26,040 --> 00:45:27,060
 ne, nego moraš pitati

1513
00:45:27,060 --> 00:45:27,540
 dozvolu,

1514
00:45:27,540 --> 00:45:28,560
 da ovodim u trgovinu,

1515
00:45:28,560 --> 00:45:29,520
 pa se tu učiš,

1516
00:45:29,520 --> 00:45:30,740
 odgajaš se u nekim stvarima,

1517
00:45:30,740 --> 00:45:32,960
 da ne tražim najprije

1518
00:45:32,960 --> 00:45:33,620
 svoje potrebe,

1519
00:45:33,620 --> 00:45:35,140
 vidim treba li to za zajednicu,

1520
00:45:35,140 --> 00:45:36,180
 je li to dobro za njih,

1521
00:45:36,180 --> 00:45:36,660
 ako je,

1522
00:45:36,660 --> 00:45:37,820
 pitaću na nadležnog

1523
00:45:37,820 --> 00:45:38,360
 da me pusti,

1524
00:45:38,380 --> 00:45:39,260
 da napravim to i tu stvar,

1525
00:45:39,260 --> 00:45:40,160
 jer je dobro za zajednicu,

1526
00:45:40,160 --> 00:45:40,420
 ne znam,

1527
00:45:40,420 --> 00:45:41,160
 je li treba mene

1528
00:45:41,160 --> 00:45:42,340
 neka osnovna potreba,

1529
00:45:42,340 --> 00:45:43,240
 pa mogu li to stvar,

1530
00:45:43,240 --> 00:45:43,960
 mogu, ne mogu,

1531
00:45:43,960 --> 00:45:45,580
 da se naučim ne puniti

1532
00:45:45,580 --> 00:45:46,200
 na te stvari,

1533
00:45:46,200 --> 00:45:47,400
 ako nije po mojoj volji,

1534
00:45:47,400 --> 00:45:49,160
 jer tu tešiš svoju volju

1535
00:45:49,160 --> 00:45:49,680
 najprije,

1536
00:45:49,680 --> 00:45:50,540
 to je najteže,

1537
00:45:50,540 --> 00:45:51,500
 a najpotrebnije

1538
00:45:51,500 --> 00:45:52,640
 i traje cijeloga života,

1539
00:45:52,640 --> 00:45:53,340
 samo tu si

1540
00:45:53,340 --> 00:45:55,300
 najizloženiji sebi

1541
00:45:55,300 --> 00:45:56,040
 i samoći

1542
00:45:56,040 --> 00:45:56,960
 da moraš to raditi

1543
00:45:56,960 --> 00:45:57,520
 sa sobom.

1544
00:45:57,520 --> 00:45:59,900
 Nakon toga slijedi

1545
00:45:59,900 --> 00:46:01,420
 studij teologije

1546
00:46:01,420 --> 00:46:02,200
 i filozofije

1547
00:46:02,200 --> 00:46:02,940
 u Zagrebu,

1548
00:46:04,460 --> 00:46:05,760
 preporučeno 5 godina,

1549
00:46:05,760 --> 00:46:06,880
 ako nekom treba duže,

1550
00:46:06,880 --> 00:46:07,540
 nije problem,

1551
00:46:07,540 --> 00:46:09,560
 ali dakle to ovisi

1552
00:46:09,560 --> 00:46:10,320
 i koliko ko uspije

1553
00:46:10,320 --> 00:46:11,300
 rješavati ispite,

1554
00:46:11,300 --> 00:46:12,760
 za to vrijeme

1555
00:46:12,760 --> 00:46:13,700
 budu pripreme

1556
00:46:13,700 --> 00:46:14,940
 za doživotne zavete

1557
00:46:14,940 --> 00:46:15,840
 koje se polože

1558
00:46:15,840 --> 00:46:16,460
 kasnije,

1559
00:46:16,460 --> 00:46:18,440
 ali to je ono,

1560
00:46:18,440 --> 00:46:19,580
 već posebna odluka,

1561
00:46:19,580 --> 00:46:20,140
 kad nakon toga

1562
00:46:20,140 --> 00:46:21,060
 ti nima veće request,

1563
00:46:21,060 --> 00:46:21,380
 ono,

1564
00:46:21,380 --> 00:46:22,380
 ili jesi ili nisi,

1565
00:46:22,380 --> 00:46:23,680
 dok se privremeni

1566
00:46:23,680 --> 00:46:24,640
 jednog unika istaknu,

1567
00:46:24,640 --> 00:46:25,840
 moraš nastaviti živjeti

1568
00:46:25,840 --> 00:46:26,340
 normalno,

1569
00:46:26,340 --> 00:46:27,460
 ne biti fratar kasnije

1570
00:46:27,460 --> 00:46:28,100
 ako ne želiješ,

1571
00:46:28,100 --> 00:46:28,740
 ali već kad imaš

1572
00:46:28,740 --> 00:46:29,460
 doživotne stvari

1573
00:46:29,460 --> 00:46:30,300
 malo ozbiljnija,

1574
00:46:30,300 --> 00:46:32,700
 da se već počinu

1575
00:46:32,700 --> 00:46:33,360
 naglednom pripreme

1576
00:46:33,360 --> 00:46:34,160
 i za ređenje,

1577
00:46:34,160 --> 00:46:34,880
 jedno drugo,

1578
00:46:34,880 --> 00:46:35,920
 tako da ono,

1579
00:46:35,920 --> 00:46:37,520
 ima dovoljno vremena

1580
00:46:37,520 --> 00:46:38,900
 da se shvatio neke stvari

1581
00:46:38,900 --> 00:46:39,580
 o sebi,

1582
00:46:39,580 --> 00:46:41,200
 jesam li za toga,

1583
00:46:41,200 --> 00:46:42,260
 jesam li zato popraviti

1584
00:46:42,260 --> 00:46:42,740
 neke stvari

1585
00:46:42,740 --> 00:46:44,140
 s kojima sam se borio,

1586
00:46:44,140 --> 00:46:46,820
 naučiti

1587
00:46:46,820 --> 00:46:48,140
 kakav je Bog

1588
00:46:48,140 --> 00:46:48,860
 prema tebi,

1589
00:46:48,860 --> 00:46:49,680
 da ga moraš

1590
00:46:49,680 --> 00:46:50,640
 navještivati drugima,

1591
00:46:50,640 --> 00:46:51,960
 ako ga nisu usre

1592
00:46:51,960 --> 00:46:52,460
 i upoznao,

1593
00:46:52,460 --> 00:46:53,800
 o čemu ćeš govoriti,

1594
00:46:53,800 --> 00:46:55,340
 tako da vjerujem

1595
00:46:55,340 --> 00:46:56,900
 da je tih 7-8 godina

1596
00:46:56,900 --> 00:46:57,780
 dovoljno

1597
00:46:57,780 --> 00:46:58,500
 da čovjek

1598
00:46:58,500 --> 00:46:59,300
 u sebi

1599
00:46:59,300 --> 00:47:00,020
 sazrije

1600
00:47:00,020 --> 00:47:00,740
 i naraste

1601
00:47:00,740 --> 00:47:02,000
 onome što je potrebno

1602
00:47:02,000 --> 00:47:03,100
 kako bi kasnije

1603
00:47:03,100 --> 00:47:03,840
 zvršio ono što

1604
00:47:03,840 --> 00:47:04,920
 Bog on ne ga traži.

1605
00:47:04,920 --> 00:47:05,740
 Ako,

1606
00:47:05,740 --> 00:47:07,200
 ono,

1607
00:47:07,200 --> 00:47:07,880
 bilo čemu toga

1608
00:47:07,880 --> 00:47:08,800
 budeš aljkav,

1609
00:47:08,800 --> 00:47:10,500
 ne trudiš se dovoljno,

1610
00:47:10,500 --> 00:47:11,600
 pogotovo ako pozva,

1611
00:47:11,600 --> 00:47:12,700
 zapustiš tu stvar,

1612
00:47:12,700 --> 00:47:14,160
 napustiš krok

1613
00:47:14,160 --> 00:47:14,940
 u mjesec dana,

1614
00:47:14,940 --> 00:47:16,180
 jer ljudi kontaju,

1615
00:47:16,180 --> 00:47:17,020
 ono,

1616
00:47:17,020 --> 00:47:18,440
 odozovi se i miran si,

1617
00:47:18,440 --> 00:47:19,460
 treba kasnije,

1618
00:47:19,460 --> 00:47:20,060
 zalirat.

1619
00:47:20,060 --> 00:47:20,600
 Tek onda počne.

1620
00:47:20,600 --> 00:47:21,000
 Znači,

1621
00:47:21,000 --> 00:47:22,300
 tada se tek posio stvar,

1622
00:47:22,300 --> 00:47:23,240
 treba zalivat,

1623
00:47:23,240 --> 00:47:25,120
 održavati

1624
00:47:25,120 --> 00:47:27,360
 da stvari nepresano rastu,

1625
00:47:27,360 --> 00:47:28,840
 da ništa se ne osuši,

1626
00:47:28,840 --> 00:47:29,560
 da ne propadne,

1627
00:47:29,560 --> 00:47:30,920
 zbog tvoga ne mara,

1628
00:47:30,920 --> 00:47:32,280
 jer Bog je posadio,

1629
00:47:32,280 --> 00:47:33,100
 dao je da nikne,

1630
00:47:33,100 --> 00:47:35,220
 ali to je da dalje držiš na životu.

1631
00:47:35,220 --> 00:47:36,320
 Tako da,

1632
00:47:36,320 --> 00:47:37,740
 to je možda najteža stvar,

1633
00:47:37,740 --> 00:47:39,200
 znat se posvijeti sebi u svemu.

1634
00:47:39,200 --> 00:47:41,320
 A jesi imao ikakva iskušenja,

1635
00:47:41,320 --> 00:47:41,740
 krize,

1636
00:47:41,740 --> 00:47:43,040
 da si bio blizu odlaska?

1637
00:47:44,200 --> 00:47:45,120
 tri puta,

1638
00:47:45,120 --> 00:47:46,900
 sam bio spremio stvari.

1639
00:47:46,900 --> 00:47:50,040
 Spremio sve u kofer.

1640
00:47:50,040 --> 00:47:51,440
 Samo treba dole smerster,

1641
00:47:51,440 --> 00:47:52,720
 pokusat navrat odgojitelju,

1642
00:47:52,720 --> 00:47:54,000
 ja bi kući.

1643
00:47:54,000 --> 00:47:56,480
 Nisam nijelo imao hrabrosti.

1644
00:47:56,480 --> 00:47:57,600
 Kad sam bio na ucijatoj,

1645
00:47:57,600 --> 00:47:58,640
 kad sam bio bogoslovi.

1646
00:47:58,640 --> 00:48:00,100
 Nisam imao hrabrosti,

1647
00:48:00,100 --> 00:48:00,920
 sam urezi te riječi,

1648
00:48:00,920 --> 00:48:01,700
 ja bi kući.

1649
00:48:01,700 --> 00:48:04,600
 Samo zbog toga sam ostao,

1650
00:48:04,600 --> 00:48:05,900
 jer sam bio kukavica.

1651
00:48:05,900 --> 00:48:08,140
 I drago mi da sam bio kukavica.

1652
00:48:08,140 --> 00:48:09,540
 Vjerujem ja da bi sada kasnije

1653
00:48:09,540 --> 00:48:10,980
 ponošao van kao svijetu.

1654
00:48:10,980 --> 00:48:12,740
 Ne bi to bio problem.

1655
00:48:13,620 --> 00:48:15,500
 Ali ne vrijem da bi bio sritan

1656
00:48:15,500 --> 00:48:16,260
 kao što sam sada.

1657
00:48:16,260 --> 00:48:17,540
 Isponjen iznutra.

1658
00:48:17,540 --> 00:48:18,640
 Da ne tražem ništa.

1659
00:48:18,640 --> 00:48:19,640
 Izvan kada mi trebalo nešto

1660
00:48:19,640 --> 00:48:20,220
 da me podikne,

1661
00:48:20,220 --> 00:48:20,900
 ne znam nija šta.

1662
00:48:20,900 --> 00:48:24,840
 Jer znam da činim nešto

1663
00:48:24,840 --> 00:48:26,240
 što je Bogu važno.

1664
00:48:26,240 --> 00:48:28,140
 Možda se meni čini

1665
00:48:28,140 --> 00:48:29,060
 malenoj,

1666
00:48:29,060 --> 00:48:30,260
 ne vidim plodove toga.

1667
00:48:30,260 --> 00:48:32,460
 A znam da to nekom božije mozaiku

1668
00:48:32,460 --> 00:48:33,580
 se ima nekog smisla.

1669
00:48:33,580 --> 00:48:34,860
 Nema meni sada,

1670
00:48:34,860 --> 00:48:36,300
 pa za neki, ne znam,

1671
00:48:36,300 --> 00:48:39,420
 20 godina karikiram.

1672
00:48:39,420 --> 00:48:40,480
 Ne znam kako će još živit,

1673
00:48:40,480 --> 00:48:41,820
 će se sve stvari posloži,

1674
00:48:41,820 --> 00:48:42,560
 pa da ja vidim,

1675
00:48:43,040 --> 00:48:44,440
 aha, ovo je stvarno imao smisla

1676
00:48:44,440 --> 00:48:45,540
 zbog ovoga i ovoga.

1677
00:48:45,540 --> 00:48:47,940
 Naša hercegovina,

1678
00:48:47,940 --> 00:48:48,780
 evo, Bogu hvala,

1679
00:48:48,780 --> 00:48:50,820
 obilije duhovnim pozivima.

1680
00:48:50,820 --> 00:48:51,940
 Pa što misliš,

1681
00:48:51,940 --> 00:48:53,700
 čemu je to razlog?

1682
00:48:53,700 --> 00:48:56,080
 Evo, imamo i naše mučenike,

1683
00:48:56,080 --> 00:48:57,560
 krl je proliveno ovdje

1684
00:48:57,560 --> 00:48:59,380
 i gospod Međugorje,

1685
00:48:59,380 --> 00:49:00,740
 sto neki od razloga.

1686
00:49:00,740 --> 00:49:01,960
 Zašto je naša provincija?

1687
00:49:02,520 --> 00:49:08,020
 Mi moramo uzeti to kao neke već pluseve,

1688
00:49:08,020 --> 00:49:10,000
 zašto imamo zvanja.

1689
00:49:10,000 --> 00:49:12,260
 Ali ja mislim da je prvo

1690
00:49:12,260 --> 00:49:15,320
 to što naša babe puno mole,

1691
00:49:15,320 --> 00:49:18,880
 što naše matere puno mole,

1692
00:49:18,880 --> 00:49:21,200
 pa i neka dica.

1693
00:49:23,260 --> 00:49:25,620
 Svako ovo zvanje je izmoljeno zvanje.

1694
00:49:25,620 --> 00:49:27,780
 Nijedno se nije rodila samo od sebe,

1695
00:49:27,780 --> 00:49:29,080
 svako je neko izmolio.

1696
00:49:29,080 --> 00:49:31,060
 Vjerujem da je to oplod

1697
00:49:31,060 --> 00:49:32,460
 najprije tih molitvi,

1698
00:49:32,460 --> 00:49:35,020
 koje su neprestancible,

1699
00:49:35,020 --> 00:49:37,060
 nije baba moja mola da budem fratar,

1700
00:49:37,060 --> 00:49:39,080
 ali mola je da Bog pošalje fratre,

1701
00:49:39,080 --> 00:49:40,800
 da pošalje svećenike.

1702
00:49:40,800 --> 00:49:42,440
 Jer narod uvijek treba,

1703
00:49:42,500 --> 00:49:43,200
 kako izmoliš,

1704
00:49:43,200 --> 00:49:44,060
 takve već ćeš dobiti.

1705
00:49:44,060 --> 00:49:46,400
 Tako da vjerujem da je to oplodi

1706
00:49:46,400 --> 00:49:47,340
 tih molitava,

1707
00:49:47,340 --> 00:49:49,760
 onda i zagovora naših mučenika,

1708
00:49:49,760 --> 00:49:54,820
 a i to da je tu prisutnost Gospina,

1709
00:49:54,820 --> 00:49:55,520
 svakako,

1710
00:49:55,520 --> 00:49:57,280
 ali ono što kaže narodna izreka,

1711
00:49:57,280 --> 00:50:00,420
 di Bog šak onda je Gospa vriću širi.

1712
00:50:00,420 --> 00:50:03,800
 Di je Bog možda nam umio desetoricu,

1713
00:50:03,800 --> 00:50:05,020
 ona će još desetoricu nam,

1714
00:50:05,020 --> 00:50:06,980
 nekako kako mater samo zna.

1715
00:50:06,980 --> 00:50:09,520
 Tako da vjerujem da ima i toga,

1716
00:50:09,520 --> 00:50:10,940
 a kad se to sve zbroji,

1717
00:50:11,320 --> 00:50:13,380
 dobijemo ovo Bogu hvala što imamo.

1718
00:50:13,380 --> 00:50:16,500
 Tu je opet radi sa Framom,

1719
00:50:16,500 --> 00:50:17,940
 koji je ono,

1720
00:50:17,940 --> 00:50:19,920
 jako dobar mogu reći nekako,

1721
00:50:19,920 --> 00:50:23,000
 gdje su fratri naučili

1722
00:50:23,000 --> 00:50:25,660
 da je dobro zbližiti se s mlađarijom,

1723
00:50:25,660 --> 00:50:27,160
 da ne treba mi daleko ljudi,

1724
00:50:27,160 --> 00:50:29,460
 nego biti tu s njima i za njih,

1725
00:50:29,460 --> 00:50:30,440
 ne samo u vrima rata,

1726
00:50:30,440 --> 00:50:31,380
 sa vrima rata prošlo,

1727
00:50:31,380 --> 00:50:33,620
 a treba i sad zna biti s njima.

1728
00:50:33,620 --> 00:50:36,820
 Tako da vjerujem da i to ima utjecaja,

1729
00:50:36,820 --> 00:50:39,420
 što smo sve mi mlazi fratri

1730
00:50:39,420 --> 00:50:41,300
 nekako približili toj čelja,

1731
00:50:41,300 --> 00:50:43,540
 da se s njima ti družiš,

1732
00:50:43,540 --> 00:50:44,360
 da ću otići s njima,

1733
00:50:44,360 --> 00:50:44,960
 ne znam i ja,

1734
00:50:44,960 --> 00:50:46,900
 odigrati nogometar,

1735
00:50:46,900 --> 00:50:48,260
 otići još na kviz s njima,

1736
00:50:48,260 --> 00:50:49,020
 ne znam šta goto.

1737
00:50:49,120 --> 00:50:52,520
 mislim da vi sad prestanete raditi s framovom ministrantima,

1738
00:50:52,520 --> 00:50:56,260
 pa vjerojatno ne bilo više fratara za nekih 50-a godina,

1739
00:50:56,260 --> 00:50:59,140
 mislim u smislu rećemo brojnosti ovaj.

1740
00:50:59,500 --> 00:51:02,460
 pa sigurno ja ne bilo do toga dođe,

1741
00:51:02,460 --> 00:51:03,760
 ne bi mi znao šta bi mi radili.

1742
00:51:03,760 --> 00:51:05,480
 Mlad sam čovjek,

1743
00:51:05,480 --> 00:51:06,920
 ja trebam nešto raditi sa sobom,

1744
00:51:06,920 --> 00:51:08,960
 trebam negdje svoje snage uložiti.

1745
00:51:09,500 --> 00:51:12,400
 Ako ih ne ulažem u služenje drugima na takav način,

1746
00:51:12,400 --> 00:51:13,140
 u šta ću ugri,

1747
00:51:13,140 --> 00:51:14,360
 onda ću ugri otići,

1748
00:51:14,360 --> 00:51:15,360
 a to ne bi volio.

1749
00:51:15,360 --> 00:51:17,400
 Pa rađe ću onda crknut od rada,

1750
00:51:17,400 --> 00:51:18,800
 da sam stalno s drugima,

1751
00:51:18,800 --> 00:51:19,940
 da s njima radim,

1752
00:51:19,940 --> 00:51:21,760
 nego da se zatvorim u sobu,

1753
00:51:21,760 --> 00:51:23,640
 uživam u nekom lagodnom životu

1754
00:51:23,640 --> 00:51:25,180
 koji mi mora biti lijep,

1755
00:51:25,180 --> 00:51:27,360
 onda ću umrati od linosti,

1756
00:51:27,360 --> 00:51:28,060
 usmrtno grijan,

1757
00:51:28,060 --> 00:51:28,880
 ovako ga nakon ne zanija,

1758
00:51:28,880 --> 00:51:29,740
 zatvorit ću se u Bog,

1759
00:51:29,740 --> 00:51:30,200
 znaš šta,

1760
00:51:30,200 --> 00:51:31,480
 Bog je na šta ću postati.

1761
00:51:31,480 --> 00:51:33,060
 Pa rađe je ovako,

1762
00:51:33,060 --> 00:51:34,440
 izginut za jednu duš,

1763
00:51:34,440 --> 00:51:35,340
 izginut za jednu duš,

1764
00:51:35,340 --> 00:51:35,880
 ako treba.

1765
00:51:35,880 --> 00:51:36,680
 Nije im problem.

1766
00:51:36,680 --> 00:51:38,380
 Tako da,

1767
00:51:38,380 --> 00:51:39,660
 to možda ima.

1768
00:51:39,660 --> 00:51:41,320
 Ja ovo sve priješao sam nabrao,

1769
00:51:41,320 --> 00:51:42,200
 dakle i temelite,

1770
00:51:42,200 --> 00:51:42,780
 i baka,

1771
00:51:42,780 --> 00:51:43,300
 i djedova,

1772
00:51:43,300 --> 00:51:44,060
 i roditelja,

1773
00:51:44,060 --> 00:51:46,220
 i gospodina prisutnosti,

1774
00:51:46,220 --> 00:51:46,960
 i zagovar mučenika,

1775
00:51:47,080 --> 00:51:48,900
 sigurno sam ima vrlo velik utjecaj.

1776
00:51:48,900 --> 00:51:51,160
 Naš rad možda 5%,

1777
00:51:51,160 --> 00:51:53,300
 ali ovo sve drugo je jako važno.

1778
00:51:53,300 --> 00:51:54,540
 Zato da nas isto jako važno,

1779
00:51:54,540 --> 00:51:56,680
 nastaviti moli za duhovna zvanja.

1780
00:51:56,680 --> 00:51:58,180
 Ko što moli naše babe,

1781
00:51:58,180 --> 00:52:00,120
 da nastave moliti materija,

1782
00:52:00,120 --> 00:52:00,840
 ali i dica,

1783
00:52:00,840 --> 00:52:02,740
 da znaju moli za duhovna zvanja.

1784
00:52:02,740 --> 00:52:04,020
 Treba će i njima kasnije,

1785
00:52:04,020 --> 00:52:04,760
 da njih neko ispovijeti,

1786
00:52:04,760 --> 00:52:05,800
 da njihoj ljudi su krsti,

1787
00:52:05,800 --> 00:52:07,240
 da njihoj njih vinčava.

1788
00:52:07,240 --> 00:52:11,360
 Da ne moramo uvojiti sa strana,

1789
00:52:11,360 --> 00:52:12,120
 što bi se reklo,

1790
00:52:12,120 --> 00:52:14,360
 nego da imamo svoje.

1791
00:52:15,680 --> 00:52:17,280
 Ti si u Dunu,

1792
00:52:17,280 --> 00:52:18,180
 u Tomislagradu,

1793
00:52:18,180 --> 00:52:19,260
 duhovni asistent Frame,

1794
00:52:19,260 --> 00:52:22,440
 pa evo, kako je tebi osobno u radu s mladim?

1795
00:52:22,440 --> 00:52:25,280
 Ja, znači...

1796
00:52:25,280 --> 00:52:26,240
 S ovaj nasom, ja.

1797
00:52:26,240 --> 00:52:28,780
 Ne mogu reći tako,

1798
00:52:28,780 --> 00:52:31,100
 bolje je od toga.

1799
00:52:31,100 --> 00:52:32,600
 Bolje je od toga,

1800
00:52:32,600 --> 00:52:35,160
 mislim, meni je gori ta služba

1801
00:52:35,160 --> 00:52:36,180
 da sam duhovni asistent,

1802
00:52:36,180 --> 00:52:37,100
 ali ja nisam sigurno

1803
00:52:37,100 --> 00:52:38,340
 da su on asistent meni

1804
00:52:38,340 --> 00:52:39,420
 ili sam ja asistent njima.

1805
00:52:39,420 --> 00:52:41,940
 Dica gori su jako dobra.

1806
00:52:41,940 --> 00:52:45,160
 I od njih jako puno učim.

1807
00:52:45,680 --> 00:52:46,560
 Nima jedna grupa,

1808
00:52:46,560 --> 00:52:50,580
 to je većina ekipa prvi i srednji rad.

1809
00:52:50,580 --> 00:52:52,940
 Znači, od mene su oni mlazi jako puno upola.

1810
00:52:52,940 --> 00:52:54,300
 Mlazi od mene,

1811
00:52:54,300 --> 00:52:56,280
 to su i dobiti slijepci.

1812
00:52:56,280 --> 00:52:58,040
 Tako se zove grupa.

1813
00:52:58,040 --> 00:52:59,700
 Idemo često na kvizove.

1814
00:52:59,700 --> 00:53:00,500
 I tu, znači,

1815
00:53:00,500 --> 00:53:01,240
 to je baš,

1816
00:53:01,240 --> 00:53:02,300
 nas je tu pet.

1817
00:53:02,300 --> 00:53:04,560
 Ali tu je jako šarena grupa ljudi.

1818
00:53:05,100 --> 00:53:07,060
 i od te četvorce.

1819
00:53:07,760 --> 00:53:09,440
 Ja svaki dan mogu naučiti.

1820
00:53:09,440 --> 00:53:11,360
 Ja jako puno.

1821
00:53:11,360 --> 00:53:12,980
 A ima je huframni slo,

1822
00:53:12,980 --> 00:53:13,260
 50,

1823
00:53:13,260 --> 00:53:14,340
 jer je doba samo sada četvorica.

1824
00:53:14,340 --> 00:53:17,240
 Koliko sam učio da nije biv sjeframasa,

1825
00:53:17,240 --> 00:53:18,380
 koji su odšli sad izluno,

1826
00:53:18,380 --> 00:53:20,000
 pa su odjelili prva drugogodina fakulteta.

1827
00:53:20,000 --> 00:53:22,120
 Koliko sam od njih puno naučio.

1828
00:53:23,000 --> 00:53:23,300
 Recimo,

1829
00:53:23,300 --> 00:53:24,380
 meni je duvno naučilo

1830
00:53:24,380 --> 00:53:28,420
 da budem iskren u lice sa svima.

1831
00:53:28,420 --> 00:53:29,880
 Nekad bi ja nekad sad prešutio,

1832
00:53:29,880 --> 00:53:31,300
 ono neću je da me neko povridio,

1833
00:53:31,300 --> 00:53:33,300
 odmah ok ću se prešutiti tu stvar.

1834
00:53:33,300 --> 00:53:36,400
 Duvno me naučilo da imam pravo reći nekome,

1835
00:53:36,400 --> 00:53:37,840
 je, to ti nije dobro.

1836
00:53:37,840 --> 00:53:40,500
 Da to mogu nekome smij reći.

1837
00:53:40,500 --> 00:53:41,920
 On će meni to reći u facu.

1838
00:53:41,920 --> 00:53:43,680
 Frater, ono ti nije bao dobro.

1839
00:53:43,680 --> 00:53:46,140
 I onda što mi ti to govoriš?

1840
00:53:46,140 --> 00:53:47,360
 A se on njih naučio,

1841
00:53:47,360 --> 00:53:48,160
 to je dobra stvar.

1842
00:53:48,160 --> 00:53:50,680
 Ono se me naučilo da je dobro plakat

1843
00:53:50,680 --> 00:53:52,980
 i pred ljudima,

1844
00:53:53,000 --> 00:53:54,040
 ja bi prije blako sam.

1845
00:53:54,040 --> 00:53:56,300
 Oni god našto nam plaću zajedno.

1846
00:53:56,300 --> 00:53:57,540
 Moletvena sekcija,

1847
00:53:57,540 --> 00:53:59,220
 većinom plaću zajedno.

1848
00:53:59,220 --> 00:54:02,760
 Naučili smo je koliko je važno

1849
00:54:02,760 --> 00:54:04,680
 imati dobro prijatelja

1850
00:54:04,680 --> 00:54:06,020
 koji će te opomenut.

1851
00:54:06,020 --> 00:54:06,680
 Nije se da govori,

1852
00:54:06,680 --> 00:54:07,800
 nego će te opomenut.

1853
00:54:07,800 --> 00:54:10,800
 E, aj, nemoj observati ružno te čut.

1854
00:54:10,800 --> 00:54:13,840
 Nemoj, ne znam, pušiti ružno te viditi.

1855
00:54:13,840 --> 00:54:14,980
 Ili bilo što drugo.

1856
00:54:14,980 --> 00:54:18,040
 Znači, koliko su ta dica gore,

1857
00:54:18,040 --> 00:54:19,900
 mene, meni pomogla.

1858
00:54:19,900 --> 00:54:22,540
 Ja sam Bogu premalo zahvalno

1859
00:54:22,540 --> 00:54:24,000
 našao sam ja na službi u Dunu.

1860
00:54:24,000 --> 00:54:25,480
 Jednostavno.

1861
00:54:25,480 --> 00:54:28,580
 Ti smošni jedan od rijetkih što se za Dunu zahvali.

1862
00:54:28,580 --> 00:54:29,560
 Ozbino.

1863
00:54:29,560 --> 00:54:32,040
 Znači, evo, što se menja tiče,

1864
00:54:32,040 --> 00:54:33,720
 ako ima negdje opcija,

1865
00:54:33,720 --> 00:54:35,420
 da popišem da sam gore do karaule,

1866
00:54:35,420 --> 00:54:37,080
 da sam do sprovoda svoga,

1867
00:54:37,080 --> 00:54:38,780
 opa, popisao.

1868
00:54:38,780 --> 00:54:40,560
 Bez razmišljanja sekunde.

1869
00:54:41,400 --> 00:54:45,920
 Meni je to Dunu toliko došlo na duhovnu korist i izgradnju

1870
00:54:45,920 --> 00:54:48,060
 da ja ne mogu opisati to riječ.

1871
00:54:48,060 --> 00:54:49,900
 Glupo je da hvalim,

1872
00:54:49,900 --> 00:54:51,380
 ali ne mogu sakrati.

1873
00:54:52,380 --> 00:54:53,760
 Ljudi po meni bili na humcu

1874
00:54:53,760 --> 00:54:54,760
 i da sam puno naučio

1875
00:54:54,760 --> 00:54:55,940
 od drugih ljudi

1876
00:54:55,940 --> 00:54:57,420
 koja sam dost usrao i upoznao

1877
00:54:57,420 --> 00:54:59,280
 i ljepotu prijateljstva i služenja.

1878
00:54:59,280 --> 00:55:00,480
 U dost prvi korac,

1879
00:55:00,480 --> 00:55:01,540
 bilo, to ne moraš zaboraviti,

1880
00:55:01,540 --> 00:55:02,780
 da si učio neke stvari.

1881
00:55:02,780 --> 00:55:05,420
 Dakle, zahvalan sam i za huma,

1882
00:55:05,420 --> 00:55:06,340
 sad sam i razumijemo.

1883
00:55:06,340 --> 00:55:07,660
 Sad sam u Dunu,

1884
00:55:07,660 --> 00:55:08,460
 pitao sam i za Duvno,

1885
00:55:08,460 --> 00:55:10,720
 tako da to što bi u Duvnu mogu reći.

1886
00:55:10,720 --> 00:55:12,320
 Da gore, sam naučio

1887
00:55:12,320 --> 00:55:14,000
 što znači bi duhovni asistent,

1888
00:55:14,840 --> 00:55:15,800
 kakav trebam biti,

1889
00:55:15,800 --> 00:55:17,420
 kako se trebam truto kod tjedice

1890
00:55:17,420 --> 00:55:20,260
 i nadam se da se niko od njih

1891
00:55:20,260 --> 00:55:21,500
 ne osjeća zakinuto,

1892
00:55:21,500 --> 00:55:24,140
 jer zaslušuju puno boljeg asistenta

1893
00:55:24,140 --> 00:55:24,980
 nego što sam ja,

1894
00:55:24,980 --> 00:55:26,320
 to im kažem sto puta.

1895
00:55:26,320 --> 00:55:28,360
 Nekaj me za to čušnu,

1896
00:55:28,360 --> 00:55:29,180
 nekad nisu,

1897
00:55:29,180 --> 00:55:30,740
 malo im toliko bi vas meta,

1898
00:55:30,740 --> 00:55:32,860
 ali ja ne volim slagat,

1899
00:55:32,860 --> 00:55:34,380
 pa neće slagat ne za te stvari.

1900
00:55:34,380 --> 00:55:37,260
 Tako da je raz mladima gore

1901
00:55:37,260 --> 00:55:38,480
 promijenio mene,

1902
00:55:38,480 --> 00:55:39,560
 možda je mijenja njih,

1903
00:55:39,560 --> 00:55:40,220
 to ne znam,

1904
00:55:40,220 --> 00:55:42,220
 ali mene je sigurno promijenio.

1905
00:55:42,220 --> 00:55:43,940
 Kako vam aframa izgleda

1906
00:55:43,940 --> 00:55:44,940
 što vi imate na aframa,

1907
00:55:44,940 --> 00:55:46,540
 ove godine je slaviti 30 godine,

1908
00:55:46,540 --> 00:55:46,980
 ali tako?

1909
00:55:46,980 --> 00:55:48,140
 Tako je, tako je,

1910
00:55:48,140 --> 00:55:49,980
 da smo do okrugljove brojke 30,

1911
00:55:49,980 --> 00:55:51,040
 aframa gore,

1912
00:55:51,040 --> 00:55:53,380
 najprije to su dica

1913
00:55:53,380 --> 00:55:54,760
 koja stalna u okotrškve.

1914
00:55:54,760 --> 00:55:57,580
 On posle škole neće kućić,

1915
00:55:57,580 --> 00:55:59,220
 on će ostati na aframi.

1916
00:55:59,220 --> 00:56:00,580
 To ne postoji,

1917
00:56:00,580 --> 00:56:01,440
 obse da ne ostanu,

1918
00:56:01,440 --> 00:56:02,820
 da neštinkaj biti posle škole tamo,

1919
00:56:02,820 --> 00:56:03,620
 to ne postoji,

1920
00:56:03,620 --> 00:56:05,280
 uvijek će neko biti tu,

1921
00:56:05,280 --> 00:56:07,220
 ili pogotovo kasno na večer,

1922
00:56:07,220 --> 00:56:08,560
 ne moraš i otrati od ono,

1923
00:56:08,560 --> 00:56:09,500
 trebaš da kličat stvari,

1924
00:56:09,580 --> 00:56:10,960
 ne možeš da se ono još tamo.

1925
00:56:10,960 --> 00:56:11,840
 Mene se bolam spava,

1926
00:56:11,840 --> 00:56:13,200
 ajte kuće te bati utro u školu,

1927
00:56:13,200 --> 00:56:14,340
 mi ćemo još.

1928
00:56:14,340 --> 00:56:16,660
 Dakle, to je najvažnije

1929
00:56:16,660 --> 00:56:17,280
 da se on druže,

1930
00:56:17,280 --> 00:56:18,280
 da su zajedno stalno.

1931
00:56:18,280 --> 00:56:19,340
 To im je važno.

1932
00:56:19,340 --> 00:56:20,780
 Onda postoji sekcija,

1933
00:56:20,780 --> 00:56:21,780
 naravno kod svakdje druge,

1934
00:56:22,500 --> 00:56:23,220
 imaš glazbenu,

1935
00:56:23,220 --> 00:56:24,060
 imaš likovnu,

1936
00:56:24,060 --> 00:56:25,000
 imaš medijesku,

1937
00:56:25,000 --> 00:56:25,980
 imaš dramsku,

1938
00:56:25,980 --> 00:56:27,020
 imaš čistačku,

1939
00:56:27,020 --> 00:56:28,000
 imaš radnu,

1940
00:56:28,000 --> 00:56:29,760
 ne zaboravit ću,

1941
00:56:29,760 --> 00:56:31,000
 ne znam sad da ne nabrajam sve,

1942
00:56:31,000 --> 00:56:32,960
 uglavnom imaju jako puno sekcija,

1943
00:56:32,960 --> 00:56:34,100
 stalno se nešto radi,

1944
00:56:34,100 --> 00:56:35,320
 nemamo živa mira,

1945
00:56:35,320 --> 00:56:36,260
 to je neprasnost nešto

1946
00:56:36,260 --> 00:56:37,320
 organizira događaja,

1947
00:56:37,320 --> 00:56:38,840
 ne znam kako više,

1948
00:56:38,840 --> 00:56:39,700
 oni stignu sve,

1949
00:56:39,700 --> 00:56:41,740
 uz školu i obitelj

1950
00:56:41,740 --> 00:56:43,000
 koji imaju obveze u kući,

1951
00:56:43,000 --> 00:56:44,280
 još usto da su stalno

1952
00:56:44,280 --> 00:56:44,860
 oko crkve,

1953
00:56:44,860 --> 00:56:46,260
 to mi je tu inka poskirano.

1954
00:56:46,260 --> 00:56:48,280
 Tako da ono,

1955
00:56:48,320 --> 00:56:49,580
 mena potučeo da radim s njima,

1956
00:56:49,580 --> 00:56:50,380
 ja radim ono,

1957
00:56:50,380 --> 00:56:52,340
 pokušavam da ja biti stalno s njima,

1958
00:56:52,340 --> 00:56:53,180
 oni su stalno s njima,

1959
00:56:53,180 --> 00:56:54,220
 pa jedni od drugih učimo,

1960
00:56:54,220 --> 00:56:55,280
 jedni smo tu za druge,

1961
00:56:55,280 --> 00:56:56,140
 to mi je najljepše,

1962
00:56:56,140 --> 00:56:57,000
 što su spremni,

1963
00:56:57,000 --> 00:56:58,360
 uskoči jedni drugima,

1964
00:56:58,360 --> 00:56:58,780
 u poodne,

1965
00:56:58,780 --> 00:56:59,140
 u poodne,

1966
00:56:59,140 --> 00:57:00,500
 jedna treba da vas lagati,

1967
00:57:00,500 --> 00:57:01,060
 ono će zovem,

1968
00:57:01,060 --> 00:57:02,400
 druge nam pomognu,

1969
00:57:02,400 --> 00:57:03,540
 pa će onda ići kod drugih,

1970
00:57:03,540 --> 00:57:04,180
 tako ono,

1971
00:57:04,180 --> 00:57:06,260
 tu su baš, baš uresni.

1972
00:57:06,260 --> 00:57:09,560
 Jedno smo do broja tog 30,

1973
00:57:09,560 --> 00:57:12,400
 već se lagano program priprema

1974
00:57:12,400 --> 00:57:14,140
 za sve generacije

1975
00:57:14,140 --> 00:57:15,980
 koje su kroz to u framu prošle,

1976
00:57:15,980 --> 00:57:18,240
 bit će program od tri dana,

1977
00:57:18,240 --> 00:57:20,460
 8. i 9. i 10. i 8.

1978
00:57:20,460 --> 00:57:21,920
 kroz svjedočanstva,

1979
00:57:21,920 --> 00:57:22,840
 predavanja,

1980
00:57:22,840 --> 00:57:23,820
 diskusije,

1981
00:57:23,820 --> 00:57:24,720
 sve te mise,

1982
00:57:24,720 --> 00:57:26,220
 molitve,

1983
00:57:26,220 --> 00:57:28,700
 zajedničko hodočašće u ASIS,

1984
00:57:28,700 --> 00:57:30,840
 ali i organizaciju

1985
00:57:30,840 --> 00:57:33,460
 koncerta humanitarnog duhovne glazbe,

1986
00:57:33,460 --> 00:57:35,820
 našto na principu od prošle godine.

1987
00:57:37,420 --> 00:57:38,640
 kako će to izgledati,

1988
00:57:38,640 --> 00:57:39,240
 taj koncert,

1989
00:57:39,240 --> 00:57:40,960
 to sam tamo mislio pit,

1990
00:57:40,960 --> 00:57:42,320
 sledeći je taj koncert,

1991
00:57:42,320 --> 00:57:44,240
 kako je prošao prošle godine,

1992
00:57:44,240 --> 00:57:45,720
 što pripremate za ovu?

1993
00:57:45,720 --> 00:57:47,680
 Prošla godina,

1994
00:57:47,680 --> 00:57:49,380
 to je priča za sebe,

1995
00:57:49,380 --> 00:57:50,760
 dakle, u to priča smo se uputili,

1996
00:57:50,760 --> 00:57:51,840
 Anton Jošimić i ja,

1997
00:57:51,840 --> 00:57:54,360
 nega sam upoznao u tom ASISu 2009,

1998
00:57:54,360 --> 00:57:55,700
 kad smo išli zajedno,

1999
00:57:55,700 --> 00:57:56,900
 tog hodočašće u ASIS,

2000
00:57:56,900 --> 00:57:58,500
 kako je to sve Bog ponovo spojio.

2001
00:57:58,500 --> 00:58:01,140
 Sjedimo nas veće

2002
00:58:01,140 --> 00:58:02,080
 spred samostana

2003
00:58:02,080 --> 00:58:03,660
 i kontamo tri pa neke stvari,

2004
00:58:03,660 --> 00:58:04,980
 a to je gori ravnatelj centra,

2005
00:58:04,980 --> 00:58:05,560
 nova nada,

2006
00:58:05,640 --> 00:58:07,880
 za tome slagaru za osobe s teškoćama u razvoju.

2007
00:58:07,880 --> 00:58:10,260
 Down sindrom i tako.

2008
00:58:10,260 --> 00:58:12,860
 I on konta,

2009
00:58:12,860 --> 00:58:13,440
 on govori,

2010
00:58:13,440 --> 00:58:14,460
 trebalo bi neke stvari,

2011
00:58:14,460 --> 00:58:15,140
 rad mi bi,

2012
00:58:15,140 --> 00:58:16,700
 centa malo po drugu neko razinu,

2013
00:58:16,700 --> 00:58:17,760
 treba proširiti prostore,

2014
00:58:17,760 --> 00:58:18,620
 treba, treba ono,

2015
00:58:18,620 --> 00:58:19,760
 nema šokleni,

2016
00:58:19,760 --> 00:58:20,620
 ti izvući novce.

2017
00:58:20,620 --> 00:58:23,480
 Mi imamo napraviti koncert.

2018
00:58:23,480 --> 00:58:25,420
 Oćemo li, oćemo.

2019
00:58:25,420 --> 00:58:26,140
 Ajde, kad ćemo,

2020
00:58:26,140 --> 00:58:27,020
 pogravimo datme,

2021
00:58:27,020 --> 00:58:28,200
 mogli bi taj tada,

2022
00:58:28,200 --> 00:58:28,540
 ajde,

2023
00:58:28,540 --> 00:58:30,080
 moremo.

2024
00:58:30,080 --> 00:58:32,400
 I ustovo smo krenuli

2025
00:58:32,400 --> 00:58:33,680
 bez ikakva iskustva,

2026
00:58:33,680 --> 00:58:34,740
 bez ikakva znalja,

2027
00:58:35,300 --> 00:58:36,040
 bez novca,

2028
00:58:36,040 --> 00:58:37,360
 bez apsolutno ničega,

2029
00:58:37,360 --> 00:58:40,000
 a s najmanje očekivanja.

2030
00:58:40,000 --> 00:58:42,580
 Ne znam šta moraš očekivati.

2031
00:58:42,580 --> 00:58:44,060
 Ni od posla,

2032
00:58:44,060 --> 00:58:45,220
 ni od ljudi,

2033
00:58:45,220 --> 00:58:45,960
 ni ne znam ni jače.

2034
00:58:45,960 --> 00:58:47,300
 radisni kad se usvrstimo.

2035
00:58:47,300 --> 00:58:48,560
 Prvi put uža,

2036
00:58:48,560 --> 00:58:49,200
 prvi put.

2037
00:58:49,200 --> 00:58:51,240
 I ništa mi,

2038
00:58:51,240 --> 00:58:52,280
 radit ćemo koncert.

2039
00:58:52,280 --> 00:58:53,600
 Ništa ja zove odma,

2040
00:58:53,600 --> 00:58:54,140
 koga bi,

2041
00:58:54,140 --> 00:58:54,960
 od izvođača,

2042
00:58:54,960 --> 00:58:56,580
 mi napravili popis izvođača,

2043
00:58:56,580 --> 00:58:57,300
 koga bi, šta bi,

2044
00:58:57,300 --> 00:58:58,260
 ja zove odma,

2045
00:58:58,260 --> 00:58:59,620
 prvi dan zoveme izvođače,

2046
00:58:59,620 --> 00:59:00,980
 smo nagovorili datum,

2047
00:59:00,980 --> 00:59:01,680
 morate li moramo,

2048
00:59:01,680 --> 00:59:02,640
 super zapiši,

2049
00:59:02,640 --> 00:59:03,060
 bla, bla.

2050
00:59:03,600 --> 00:59:04,680
 Eto imamo izvođače,

2051
00:59:04,680 --> 00:59:06,320
 šta sad trebamo?

2052
00:59:06,320 --> 00:59:08,500
 Pa trebalo bi on govoriti,

2053
00:59:08,500 --> 00:59:09,980
 binu, razdost, razdost,

2054
00:59:09,980 --> 00:59:10,940
 aha, to mi rođa,

2055
00:59:10,940 --> 00:59:11,560
 ako nešto radi,

2056
00:59:11,560 --> 00:59:12,280
 izvaću ja njega.

2057
00:59:12,280 --> 00:59:14,320
 Tatum je jedva slobodan.

2058
00:59:14,320 --> 00:59:15,300
 Ja znam če,

2059
00:59:15,300 --> 00:59:15,960
 da on nije mogao,

2060
00:59:15,960 --> 00:59:16,920
 ne znam ko bi nam došao.

2061
00:59:16,920 --> 00:59:18,740
 Ova, ništa napravili,

2062
00:59:18,740 --> 00:59:20,060
 to onda napravili plakat,

2063
00:59:20,060 --> 00:59:21,540
 napravili ulaznice,

2064
00:59:21,540 --> 00:59:22,620
 trebuje se prodavati.

2065
00:59:22,620 --> 00:59:24,360
 Mi je pusli,

2066
00:59:24,360 --> 00:59:25,300
 prodavio svati kontrač,

2067
00:59:25,300 --> 00:59:26,220
 šta će to planiti?

2068
00:59:26,220 --> 00:59:28,500
 Ono, takav koncert nije u Dunu bio,

2069
00:59:28,500 --> 00:59:29,520
 Bog zna odkad.

2070
00:59:30,200 --> 00:59:31,340
 Nešto je humanitarno karakter,

2071
00:59:31,340 --> 00:59:32,780
 da po ono ljudi zgodi baš na te stvari

2072
00:59:32,780 --> 00:59:33,840
 osvjetljivi i pomoći.

2073
00:59:33,840 --> 00:59:36,220
 Svi pričaju oćama, oćama ićama,

2074
00:59:36,220 --> 00:59:37,220
 a neko ulazice ne kupuje.

2075
00:59:37,220 --> 00:59:38,000
 To je bolno.

2076
00:59:38,000 --> 00:59:39,120
 Znači, koncert za tijelan dana,

2077
00:59:39,120 --> 00:59:40,500
 ono mi je padalo tisću ulaznica,

2078
00:59:40,500 --> 00:59:41,780
 ne oni za troškove.

2079
00:59:41,780 --> 00:59:43,960
 Šta ću ja daći sam?

2080
00:59:43,960 --> 00:59:45,960
 Zadnji dan,

2081
00:59:45,960 --> 00:59:48,140
 da je bilo još dupla ulaznica,

2082
00:59:48,140 --> 00:59:48,860
 otršlo bi to.

2083
00:59:48,860 --> 00:59:51,200
 A dobro, stan danu naše narode.

2084
00:59:51,200 --> 00:59:52,100
 Tako je, tako je.

2085
00:59:52,100 --> 00:59:53,420
 Tako je to nadmašla.

2086
00:59:53,420 --> 00:59:54,540
 Sva je naša moguća,

2087
00:59:54,600 --> 00:59:56,480
 očekivanja i neočekivanja.

2088
00:59:56,480 --> 00:59:58,880
 Još ljudi dali kasnije donacije,

2089
00:59:58,880 --> 01:00:00,180
 van ulaznica i toga,

2090
01:00:00,180 --> 01:00:02,360
 svega da pomognu samu akciju.

2091
01:00:02,360 --> 01:00:04,460
 Skupilo se preko sto tisuća maraka.

2092
01:00:04,460 --> 01:00:07,280
 Znači, to nismo mogli sanjati,

2093
01:00:07,280 --> 01:00:08,460
 on i ja, ni u snovima,

2094
01:00:08,460 --> 01:00:09,960
 na luđina će se skupiti toliko.

2095
01:00:09,960 --> 01:00:11,240
 Nama je bilo na kraju,

2096
01:00:11,240 --> 01:00:12,640
 ono, kad je to sve se približilo,

2097
01:00:12,640 --> 01:00:14,080
 samo da pokrijemo toškove,

2098
01:00:14,080 --> 01:00:15,140
 drugo nam ne treba.

2099
01:00:15,140 --> 01:00:17,200
 Samo da budemo na nuli drugo.

2100
01:00:17,200 --> 01:00:18,720
 Ako bude marka više, super,

2101
01:00:18,720 --> 01:00:20,780
 ali da nam je nulu izvud.

2102
01:00:20,780 --> 01:00:23,140
 Ali toliko su nas ljudi,

2103
01:00:23,260 --> 01:00:24,440
 šahmatirali, ono,

2104
01:00:24,440 --> 01:00:26,340
 mi samo kasnije sidimo i plačemo,

2105
01:00:26,340 --> 01:00:28,380
 ono, ne moraš mira kako je Bog,

2106
01:00:28,380 --> 01:00:29,200
 veliko potome sve.

2107
01:00:29,200 --> 01:00:31,960
 Tako da je ta priča ispogleda jako fina.

2108
01:00:31,960 --> 01:00:34,340
 Ove godi idemo na sličnu stvar.

2109
01:00:34,340 --> 01:00:36,320
 Od izvođača,

2110
01:00:36,320 --> 01:00:39,120
 dakle, prvo smo pozvali band

2111
01:00:39,120 --> 01:00:42,280
 i zbor iz Splita.

2112
01:00:42,280 --> 01:00:44,600
 To je zbor

2113
01:00:44,600 --> 01:00:46,860
 Visverita, Sveterna,

2114
01:00:46,860 --> 01:00:50,140
 i njihov pratijeći band.

2115
01:00:50,140 --> 01:00:52,460
 Sad ću slagat za ime

2116
01:00:52,460 --> 01:00:53,440
 Amadeo,

2117
01:00:53,440 --> 01:00:53,800
 Amadeo,

2118
01:00:53,800 --> 01:00:55,780
 nešto je tako oprosti,

2119
01:00:55,780 --> 01:00:57,580
 kar još nisam zapaniti ime do kraja.

2120
01:00:57,580 --> 01:00:59,660
 Objavljaju s pjesmu neki dan sa Framarnom,

2121
01:00:59,660 --> 01:01:00,120
 oprostim,

2122
01:01:00,120 --> 01:01:01,380
 pa tamo piše naziv benda,

2123
01:01:01,380 --> 01:01:02,360
 morate biti tamo.

2124
01:01:02,360 --> 01:01:05,320
 Sad da ja ne bih baš krivo rekao,

2125
01:01:05,320 --> 01:01:06,440
 tamo piše točno.

2126
01:01:06,440 --> 01:01:08,740
 Dakle, njih smo zvali kao prvi izvođač.

2127
01:01:08,740 --> 01:01:10,460
 s njima dolazi naravno njihova Albina,

2128
01:01:10,460 --> 01:01:13,840
 njih dolaze naš Framariš koji pjevaju ove godine kod njih.

2129
01:01:15,260 --> 01:01:16,920
 Dolazi nam Džura Ravenšćak,

2130
01:01:16,920 --> 01:01:18,420
 dolazi

2131
01:01:18,420 --> 01:01:20,420
 Stjepan Lah,

2132
01:01:20,420 --> 01:01:24,040
 bit će s nama je Framarin Karačić i Vanessa Mioć,

2133
01:01:24,040 --> 01:01:25,300
 on dolaze u kompletu.

2134
01:01:25,300 --> 01:01:28,720
 Oni su baš htjeli doći ponovo.

2135
01:01:28,720 --> 01:01:31,400
 Bilo s prošle godine i razložili da dođu ponovo,

2136
01:01:31,400 --> 01:01:33,160
 ono ja sam Framarin spominio koncert,

2137
01:01:33,160 --> 01:01:35,000
 molim da te zapiš me ove godine.

2138
01:01:35,000 --> 01:01:36,020
 Nije problema,

2139
01:01:36,020 --> 01:01:36,480
 rekao,

2140
01:01:36,480 --> 01:01:37,500
 vrlo rado.

2141
01:01:37,500 --> 01:01:38,440
 I onda me rekao,

2142
01:01:38,440 --> 01:01:39,320
 ja zovni Ivanesu,

2143
01:01:39,320 --> 01:01:40,480
 jednostavno zovni Ivanesu,

2144
01:01:40,480 --> 01:01:41,000
 tako da,

2145
01:01:41,000 --> 01:01:43,260
 i sad imaju duet on,

2146
01:01:43,260 --> 01:01:43,760
 Ivanese,

2147
01:01:43,760 --> 01:01:44,940
 imaju Vanessa i Džuro,

2148
01:01:44,940 --> 01:01:45,300
 imaju,

2149
01:01:45,300 --> 01:01:47,380
 svi troje imaju duete među se,

2150
01:01:47,380 --> 01:01:48,440
 pa neko otprilo nešto zajedno,

2151
01:01:48,440 --> 01:01:48,880
 još bolje,

2152
01:01:48,880 --> 01:01:49,680
 jer bit će još finije.

2153
01:01:49,680 --> 01:01:50,940
 Tako da,

2154
01:01:50,940 --> 01:01:53,340
 bit će to neka fina priča

2155
01:01:53,340 --> 01:01:55,120
 i ustalo će biti nastupat,

2156
01:01:55,120 --> 01:01:55,520
 naravno,

2157
01:01:55,520 --> 01:01:57,140
 iz Boruframme i Tomislavgrad,

2158
01:01:57,140 --> 01:01:58,920
 koji ovim pogodom spremaju

2159
01:01:58,920 --> 01:01:59,580
 i novi CD,

2160
01:01:59,580 --> 01:02:00,500
 odnosno album,

2161
01:02:00,500 --> 01:02:03,340
 sa 11 ili 10 pjesama,

2162
01:02:03,340 --> 01:02:03,940
 nismo možda sigurni

2163
01:02:03,940 --> 01:02:04,560
 koje način moramo.

2164
01:02:04,560 --> 01:02:05,500
 Spremano je 11 pjesama,

2165
01:02:05,500 --> 01:02:06,480
 koga ćemo izdati ne znamo,

2166
01:02:06,480 --> 01:02:07,980
 još razmišljamo tu,

2167
01:02:07,980 --> 01:02:08,340
 ali evo,

2168
01:02:08,340 --> 01:02:09,860
 glavnom sprema se nešto novo,

2169
01:02:09,860 --> 01:02:11,800
 to ćemo tom prigodom

2170
01:02:11,800 --> 01:02:13,040
 i prestaviti par pjesama,

2171
01:02:13,040 --> 01:02:14,400
 nećemo pjevati se daće predugo,

2172
01:02:14,400 --> 01:02:16,340
 pa ćemo uzeti samo par nekih stvari,

2173
01:02:16,340 --> 01:02:16,920
 i to je to.

2174
01:02:16,920 --> 01:02:18,600
 Tako da očekujemo

2175
01:02:18,600 --> 01:02:19,900
 finu priču,

2176
01:02:19,900 --> 01:02:23,060
 da sastavimo jako fine stvari zajedno,

2177
01:02:23,060 --> 01:02:25,580
 da učinimo dobro djelo

2178
01:02:25,580 --> 01:02:26,780
 za nekoga drugoga,

2179
01:02:26,780 --> 01:02:29,600
 jer Frama nema svrhu sama sebi,

2180
01:02:29,600 --> 01:02:31,140
 ako ne služi zajednicu,

2181
01:02:31,140 --> 01:02:32,220
 tako da smo odlučili

2182
01:02:32,220 --> 01:02:33,340
 taj nođaj na 30-i

2183
01:02:33,340 --> 01:02:34,560
 posveći drugima

2184
01:02:34,560 --> 01:02:36,440
 koji su zajednici potrebni,

2185
01:02:36,440 --> 01:02:37,140
 naše pomoci,

2186
01:02:37,140 --> 01:02:37,640
 a to opet,

2187
01:02:37,640 --> 01:02:38,360
 taj centar,

2188
01:02:38,360 --> 01:02:39,440
 gdje imaju jako,

2189
01:02:39,440 --> 01:02:40,620
 jako plemenito ide naprema

2190
01:02:40,620 --> 01:02:41,680
 gore i stacionar

2191
01:02:41,680 --> 01:02:43,820
 za te ljude,

2192
01:02:43,820 --> 01:02:45,220
 kad njim staratelji umru,

2193
01:02:45,220 --> 01:02:45,920
 roditelji umru,

2194
01:02:45,920 --> 01:02:46,660
 di će oni

2195
01:02:46,660 --> 01:02:48,500
 da mogu tu uživiti.

2196
01:02:48,600 --> 01:02:50,180
 da se nekoliko njima brinuti,

2197
01:02:50,180 --> 01:02:51,120
 da tu imaju,

2198
01:02:51,120 --> 01:02:51,400
 ja znam,

2199
01:02:51,400 --> 01:02:52,540
 blizu i trgovini to,

2200
01:02:52,540 --> 01:02:53,440
 pa da ih osjećaju

2201
01:02:53,440 --> 01:02:54,940
 da su dio neke zajednice,

2202
01:02:54,940 --> 01:02:56,560
 jednostavno,

2203
01:02:56,560 --> 01:02:59,060
 da su jednaki

2204
01:02:59,060 --> 01:02:59,600
 ko ostali,

2205
01:02:59,600 --> 01:03:00,620
 da se ne osjećaju

2206
01:03:00,620 --> 01:03:01,740
 isključno zato što ih nema

2207
01:03:01,740 --> 01:03:02,600
 kod negdje odvesti,

2208
01:03:02,600 --> 01:03:04,180
 da mogu sami sebe odvesti

2209
01:03:04,180 --> 01:03:04,600
 u kafić,

2210
01:03:04,600 --> 01:03:05,740
 samo tamo,

2211
01:03:05,740 --> 01:03:07,100
 jako plemenita želja,

2212
01:03:07,100 --> 01:03:08,040
 da reko,

2213
01:03:08,040 --> 01:03:09,120
 idemo,

2214
01:03:09,120 --> 01:03:09,620
 ludi smo,

2215
01:03:09,620 --> 01:03:10,060
 bojica,

2216
01:03:10,060 --> 01:03:10,880
 ajmo to napraviti.

2217
01:03:10,880 --> 01:03:11,440
 Dakle da smo

2218
01:03:11,440 --> 01:03:12,420
 i ove godine koncert

2219
01:03:12,420 --> 01:03:13,600
 na tu nakano raditi,

2220
01:03:13,600 --> 01:03:15,340
 da se skupi još sredstava,

2221
01:03:15,440 --> 01:03:16,840
 da ta priča može ići dalje.

2222
01:03:16,840 --> 01:03:18,180
 Bog hvala,

2223
01:03:18,180 --> 01:03:19,340
 a kojeg je to datom,

2224
01:03:19,340 --> 01:03:20,260
 koji je datom koncertu?

2225
01:03:20,260 --> 01:03:21,040
 10. i osmog,

2226
01:03:21,040 --> 01:03:21,940
 isto kao prošle godine,

2227
01:03:21,940 --> 01:03:22,980
 tako je ve godine koncert,

2228
01:03:22,980 --> 01:03:24,160
 10. i osmog nedelja,

2229
01:03:24,160 --> 01:03:25,660
 večerni sati,

2230
01:03:25,660 --> 01:03:26,880
 kod crkve u Dunu.

2231
01:03:26,880 --> 01:03:27,920
 Jeste ulaznice već

2232
01:03:27,920 --> 01:03:28,620
 pustili u prodaju?

2233
01:03:28,620 --> 01:03:29,120
 Nismo još,

2234
01:03:29,120 --> 01:03:29,560
 nismo još,

2235
01:03:29,560 --> 01:03:30,540
 bit će uskoro ovih dana,

2236
01:03:30,540 --> 01:03:32,340
 nećemo žurit,

2237
01:03:32,340 --> 01:03:33,500
 ono,

2238
01:03:33,500 --> 01:03:34,840
 ne potrebe da žurimo,

2239
01:03:34,840 --> 01:03:36,140
 a sad će biti

2240
01:03:36,140 --> 01:03:37,480
 ovaj koncert u Mostaru 31.

2241
01:03:37,480 --> 01:03:40,780
 pa da ne bude poklapanja,

2242
01:03:40,780 --> 01:03:41,520
 onda ćemo,

2243
01:03:41,640 --> 01:03:43,060
 odvojit ćemo te dvi priče,

2244
01:03:43,060 --> 01:03:44,100
 čisto da,

2245
01:03:44,100 --> 01:03:44,420
 ono,

2246
01:03:44,420 --> 01:03:45,480
 ispoštujemo.

2247
01:03:45,480 --> 01:03:47,760
 Mislim da dođe kupite ove godine na vrijeme,

2248
01:03:47,760 --> 01:03:49,100
 da se ne sekiraju toliko.

2249
01:03:49,100 --> 01:03:50,020
 Neću se da sekirat,

2250
01:03:50,020 --> 01:03:51,260
 dakle, sad zadnji dan da kupuju,

2251
01:03:51,260 --> 01:03:52,620
 apsolutno mi je sve jedno kazan,

2252
01:03:52,620 --> 01:03:53,240
 da će doći,

2253
01:03:53,240 --> 01:03:53,640
 ono,

2254
01:03:53,640 --> 01:03:54,300
 sve jedno mi je.

2255
01:03:54,300 --> 01:03:54,620
 Da,

2256
01:03:54,620 --> 01:03:55,540
 evo,

2257
01:03:55,540 --> 01:03:56,200
 evo,

2258
01:03:56,200 --> 01:03:58,220
 još bi jednu temu prešao,

2259
01:03:58,220 --> 01:03:59,200
 evo,

2260
01:03:59,200 --> 01:04:01,700
 mi ovo snimamo u četvrtak večera,

2261
01:04:01,700 --> 01:04:04,280
 a u četvrtak večera je izabran

2262
01:04:04,280 --> 01:04:05,400
 i novi papa,

2263
01:04:05,400 --> 01:04:08,140
 a mi smo taj izbor pratili,

2264
01:04:08,140 --> 01:04:12,220
 ponajviše zbog nekih tehničkih poteškoća

2265
01:04:12,220 --> 01:04:14,180
 i stvari s kojima smo mučili

2266
01:04:14,180 --> 01:04:15,880
 oko snimanja,

2267
01:04:15,880 --> 01:04:17,660
 ali evo da malo prokomentiramo

2268
01:04:17,660 --> 01:04:18,260
 i to,

2269
01:04:18,260 --> 01:04:20,440
 novi papa,

2270
01:04:20,440 --> 01:04:23,220
 Robert Francis Prevost,

2271
01:04:23,220 --> 01:04:24,000
 je li tako?

2272
01:04:24,000 --> 01:04:24,940
 Tako je.

2273
01:04:24,940 --> 01:04:26,820
 Papa Leon,

2274
01:04:26,820 --> 01:04:28,440
 Leon 14,

2275
01:04:28,440 --> 01:04:30,080
 sad hoće li biti Leon Love,

2276
01:04:30,080 --> 01:04:32,060
 kako se to u našćicat?

2277
01:04:32,760 --> 01:04:34,160
 Mešćini svugdje piše Love,

2278
01:04:34,160 --> 01:04:35,760
 pa ćemo ostaviti da bude Love,

2279
01:04:35,760 --> 01:04:37,340
 da ne bi mi nešto krivo najavili,

2280
01:04:37,340 --> 01:04:38,920
 gdje sam god pogledal internetu,

2281
01:04:38,920 --> 01:04:40,240
 malo prije svugdje je pisalo Love,

2282
01:04:40,240 --> 01:04:41,220
 ostavit ćemo da je Love.

2283
01:04:41,220 --> 01:04:42,700
 Papa Amerikanac,

2284
01:04:42,700 --> 01:04:43,880
 malo neočekivano.

2285
01:04:43,880 --> 01:04:45,660
 Sad oni Trump u kombinaciji

2286
01:04:45,660 --> 01:04:46,060
 protiv,

2287
01:04:46,060 --> 01:04:47,780
 tamo protiv Rusa i Ukrajine,

2288
01:04:47,780 --> 01:04:49,460
 to će biti zanimljivo sami.

2289
01:04:49,460 --> 01:04:52,380
 Ali opet se stvarilo ovo što se govori,

2290
01:04:52,380 --> 01:04:54,440
 tko u Konklavu uđe kao papa,

2291
01:04:54,440 --> 01:04:55,680
 izađe kao kardinal,

2292
01:04:55,680 --> 01:04:58,200
 on je malo iz Pozari ne došao,

2293
01:04:58,200 --> 01:04:58,780
 nije spominjano.

2294
01:04:58,800 --> 01:05:00,420
 Nikoga nije spominjano na kraju izađe,

2295
01:05:00,420 --> 01:05:01,900
 pojavio se ako papa čovječe.

2296
01:05:01,900 --> 01:05:03,600
 A svana imena koja je spominjala,

2297
01:05:03,600 --> 01:05:05,500
 deset imena se spominjalo.

2298
01:05:05,500 --> 01:05:06,540
 On je ti jedno,

2299
01:05:06,540 --> 01:05:07,580
 ti deset nije bio.

2300
01:05:07,580 --> 01:05:08,580
 Parolin je najviše,

2301
01:05:08,580 --> 01:05:09,580
 ona iz Filipina,

2302
01:05:09,580 --> 01:05:10,360
 tegle,

2303
01:05:10,360 --> 01:05:11,280
 tako veći.

2304
01:05:11,360 --> 01:05:12,720
 Ja, njega sam još spominjalo

2305
01:05:12,720 --> 01:05:14,860
 i Parolina i Pizabalu,

2306
01:05:14,860 --> 01:05:17,080
 ali na kraju Nikolji je trojice čovječe.

2307
01:05:17,080 --> 01:05:17,500
 A dobro,

2308
01:05:17,500 --> 01:05:18,260
 Bogu hvala.

2309
01:05:18,260 --> 01:05:19,160
 Hoći to duh puše,

2310
01:05:19,160 --> 01:05:20,020
 stvarno gdje hoće,

2311
01:05:20,020 --> 01:05:20,860
 ne tamo gdje hoće mi,

2312
01:05:20,860 --> 01:05:21,880
 ne gdje hoće on,

2313
01:05:21,880 --> 01:05:23,300
 gdje hoće Bog na kraju krajeva,

2314
01:05:23,300 --> 01:05:24,760
 pa bude što treba bit,

2315
01:05:24,760 --> 01:05:25,700
 nešto mi želimo.

2316
01:05:25,700 --> 01:05:28,540
 Da općenito malo prokomentiramo to papi,

2317
01:05:28,540 --> 01:05:28,740
 insko,

2318
01:05:28,740 --> 01:05:29,420
 tko je papa?

2319
01:05:29,420 --> 01:05:30,420
 Svi znamo

2320
01:05:30,420 --> 01:05:32,620
 da je Krist crkvu temeljio

2321
01:05:32,620 --> 01:05:33,780
 na Petru,

2322
01:05:33,780 --> 01:05:34,380
 kada je rekao,

2323
01:05:34,380 --> 01:05:35,680
 ti si Petar Stijena,

2324
01:05:36,440 --> 01:05:38,200
 na tebi će sagrati svoju crkvu.

2325
01:05:38,200 --> 01:05:39,500
 Svićaš šta mu je rekao

2326
01:05:39,500 --> 01:05:41,560
 najboljaki četvrtak u Maslinskom vrtu?

2327
01:05:41,560 --> 01:05:45,520
 Na koje točno misliš?

2328
01:05:45,520 --> 01:05:47,640
 Sotona će te izrašetiti,

2329
01:05:47,640 --> 01:05:48,760
 ali ja sam molio za tebe,

2330
01:05:48,760 --> 01:05:51,320
 a ti kad dođeš sve,

2331
01:05:51,320 --> 01:05:52,540
 čovrsti braći svoje.

2332
01:05:52,540 --> 01:05:53,800
 I to je najvažnije,

2333
01:05:53,800 --> 01:05:56,540
 da papa učvršćuje ljude u vjeri.

2334
01:05:56,540 --> 01:06:00,580
 Preko biskupa i nas ostale,

2335
01:06:00,580 --> 01:06:02,340
 to je glavni zadatak,

2336
01:06:02,340 --> 01:06:03,500
 da čuva polog vjere.

2337
01:06:03,500 --> 01:06:06,380
 Ono što je Krist predao crkvi,

2338
01:06:06,440 --> 01:06:07,320
 kao nauk,

2339
01:06:07,320 --> 01:06:10,260
 on je prvi koji ga mora braniti.

2340
01:06:10,260 --> 01:06:13,760
 I pisanom riječju,

2341
01:06:13,760 --> 01:06:14,580
 i govorom,

2342
01:06:14,580 --> 01:06:16,680
 a ako treba je životom poginut

2343
01:06:16,680 --> 01:06:19,600
 za tu istinu koju nam je Bog ostavio,

2344
01:06:19,600 --> 01:06:21,080
 poginut će životom za tu istinu

2345
01:06:21,080 --> 01:06:22,020
 koju nam je Bog ostavio.

2346
01:06:22,020 --> 01:06:24,260
 Jamac je jedinstva

2347
01:06:24,260 --> 01:06:28,120
 svih katolika na cijelom svijetu,

2348
01:06:28,120 --> 01:06:29,120
 koje god dobre da one bije,

2349
01:06:29,120 --> 01:06:30,500
 istočnog ili zapadnog.

2350
01:06:30,500 --> 01:06:32,680
 Papa je jamac jedinstva,

2351
01:06:32,680 --> 01:06:34,340
 koji je oko njega,

2352
01:06:34,340 --> 01:06:35,720
 oko Krista je,

2353
01:06:35,820 --> 01:06:36,600
 oko jedinstva.

2354
01:06:36,600 --> 01:06:38,540
 Ako Krist je ostavio jednu crkvu,

2355
01:06:38,540 --> 01:06:40,280
 nije ostavio tisuću crkave,

2356
01:06:40,280 --> 01:06:41,140
 ostavio jednu.

2357
01:06:41,140 --> 01:06:44,560
 Za koju mi vjerujemo da je katolička.

2358
01:06:44,560 --> 01:06:48,600
 Onda ako je zajedništvo s njima,

2359
01:06:48,600 --> 01:06:49,640
 zajedništvo je s Kristom,

2360
01:06:49,640 --> 01:06:50,340
 što se nas tiče,

2361
01:06:50,340 --> 01:06:51,560
 naravno ima drugi crkva,

2362
01:06:51,560 --> 01:06:52,120
 koje mi,

2363
01:06:52,120 --> 01:06:53,560
 ovo je glupo reći,

2364
01:06:53,560 --> 01:06:55,640
 priznajemo da su pravovaljane,

2365
01:06:55,640 --> 01:06:56,700
 da vrijede,

2366
01:06:56,700 --> 01:06:57,600
 pravoslavna crkva,

2367
01:06:57,660 --> 01:06:58,000
 na primjer.

2368
01:06:58,000 --> 01:07:00,380
 To mi je glupo reći,

2369
01:07:00,380 --> 01:07:01,960
 da smo isto ukršćani kao i oni,

2370
01:07:01,960 --> 01:07:05,040
 samo zbog nekih neslaganja u nekim stvarima,

2371
01:07:05,040 --> 01:07:06,520
 smo se morali razdvojiti,

2372
01:07:06,520 --> 01:07:07,740
 što nema smisla,

2373
01:07:07,740 --> 01:07:08,360
 tako je kako je.

2374
01:07:08,820 --> 01:07:11,400
 Dakle, Papa je amac jedinstva u to vrijeme.

2375
01:07:11,400 --> 01:07:15,240
 On je onaj koji ima moć,

2376
01:07:15,240 --> 01:07:16,800
 koja se rijeko koristi,

2377
01:07:16,800 --> 01:07:17,800
 ali ima moć,

2378
01:07:17,800 --> 01:07:20,300
 svojom riječi odrediti neke stvari

2379
01:07:20,300 --> 01:07:21,600
 kako trebaju biti.

2380
01:07:21,600 --> 01:07:23,900
 Kada, na primjer, govori ex katedra,

2381
01:07:23,900 --> 01:07:26,480
 to je bilo da sad jako malo puta,

2382
01:07:26,480 --> 01:07:29,220
 naučava neke stvari

2383
01:07:29,220 --> 01:07:31,740
 koje je crkva prepozna kroz povijest

2384
01:07:31,740 --> 01:07:34,200
 kao autentične i dostojne vjerovanja,

2385
01:07:34,200 --> 01:07:35,320
 da ih moramo vjerovat.

2386
01:07:35,320 --> 01:07:35,800
 Na primjer,

2387
01:07:35,800 --> 01:07:38,440
 kad je proglašavao dogmu Marino

2388
01:07:38,440 --> 01:07:39,760
 bezgrišnom začejeću,

2389
01:07:39,760 --> 01:07:41,660
 to je bio govore ex katedra,

2390
01:07:41,660 --> 01:07:44,700
 nauku koju svaki katolik

2391
01:07:44,700 --> 01:07:45,280
 mora vjerovat,

2392
01:07:45,280 --> 01:07:47,080
 ako želi biti dio katoličke crkve.

2393
01:07:47,080 --> 01:07:49,500
 Također, ima vlast,

2394
01:07:49,500 --> 01:07:50,640
 sudsku vlast,

2395
01:07:50,640 --> 01:07:52,400
 da nekoga razriješi nečega,

2396
01:07:52,400 --> 01:07:54,280
 ali da ga sveže za nešto,

2397
01:07:54,280 --> 01:07:56,300
 ali što je njemu pridržano,

2398
01:07:56,300 --> 01:07:57,880
 što je rekao Petru Isus,

2399
01:07:57,880 --> 01:07:59,000
 što svežeš na zemlji,

2400
01:07:59,000 --> 01:08:00,560
 sve da je na nubesima i obrnuto.

2401
01:08:00,560 --> 01:08:03,520
 Tako da i taj vlast

2402
01:08:03,520 --> 01:08:04,440
 u njegovim rukama

2403
01:08:04,440 --> 01:08:07,080
 ima vlast promijen zakone u crkvi

2404
01:08:07,080 --> 01:08:09,020
 koji nisu božanskog zakona,

2405
01:08:09,020 --> 01:08:11,000
 nego ne koji su drugačije.

2406
01:08:11,000 --> 01:08:12,480
 Drugačije naravi,

2407
01:08:12,480 --> 01:08:13,500
 to može promijeniti

2408
01:08:13,500 --> 01:08:15,120
 ako smatra potrebni.

2409
01:08:15,120 --> 01:08:16,820
 Minjalo se zakon crkve

2410
01:08:16,820 --> 01:08:17,820
 nijako puno puta,

2411
01:08:17,820 --> 01:08:19,540
 tako da može i ovaj,

2412
01:08:19,540 --> 01:08:20,480
 minjeno što god hoće,

2413
01:08:20,480 --> 01:08:22,100
 što je podlažno promijenama.

2414
01:08:22,100 --> 01:08:23,700
 Ne može promijeniti neke stvari

2415
01:08:23,700 --> 01:08:24,720
 koje su božanskog prava,

2416
01:08:24,720 --> 01:08:25,900
 da ne znam

2417
01:08:25,900 --> 01:08:28,060
 što je Bog ustanovio,

2418
01:08:28,060 --> 01:08:29,040
 da čovjek nema pravo ubiti,

2419
01:08:29,040 --> 01:08:30,040
 da mora reći sada papa,

2420
01:08:30,420 --> 01:08:31,740
 ovog čovjeka moraš ubiti,

2421
01:08:31,740 --> 01:08:33,620
 ako je to papa ne može reći.

2422
01:08:33,620 --> 01:08:35,900
 Ali te neke stvari

2423
01:08:35,900 --> 01:08:37,300
 koje papa može promijeniti,

2424
01:08:37,300 --> 01:08:38,260
 to naravno da može.

2425
01:08:38,260 --> 01:08:40,600
 Druge stvari,

2426
01:08:40,600 --> 01:08:43,340
 dok posjećuje neke semlje,

2427
01:08:43,340 --> 01:08:44,080
 neke države,

2428
01:08:44,080 --> 01:08:45,740
 počvršćuje tu braću i vjeri,

2429
01:08:45,740 --> 01:08:47,340
 vraća nadu,

2430
01:08:47,340 --> 01:08:48,200
 vraća mir,

2431
01:08:48,200 --> 01:08:50,160
 vraća čovjeku neku radost,

2432
01:08:50,160 --> 01:08:51,360
 ono nisam zaboravljen,

2433
01:08:51,360 --> 01:08:52,500
 nekad ne znam,

2434
01:08:53,060 --> 01:08:54,600
 država zabačena,

2435
01:08:54,600 --> 01:08:55,880
 ne ovdje će na kart,

2436
01:08:55,880 --> 01:08:56,820
 pa pode tamo.

2437
01:08:56,820 --> 01:08:58,860
 To je baš nekako i,

2438
01:08:58,860 --> 01:08:59,980
 pokojnog pape Franja,

2439
01:08:59,980 --> 01:09:00,820
 bio je neki cilj

2440
01:09:00,820 --> 01:09:02,180
 ići u takve države.

2441
01:09:02,180 --> 01:09:03,460
 On je baš išla samo,

2442
01:09:03,460 --> 01:09:06,020
 samo na margine.

2443
01:09:06,020 --> 01:09:07,540
 U Hrvatskoj nije bio,

2444
01:09:07,540 --> 01:09:08,980
 bio je u Bosni i Hercegovini.

2445
01:09:08,980 --> 01:09:10,740
 Bio je u Raku,

2446
01:09:10,740 --> 01:09:11,320
 bio je, ne znam,

2447
01:09:11,320 --> 01:09:11,980
 u Mijanmaru,

2448
01:09:11,980 --> 01:09:12,360
 bio je,

2449
01:09:12,360 --> 01:09:13,680
 dosta je vodao po Africi,

2450
01:09:13,680 --> 01:09:14,260
 po Aziji,

2451
01:09:14,260 --> 01:09:15,800
 te drugi nisu išli,

2452
01:09:15,800 --> 01:09:16,460
 on je išao.

2453
01:09:16,460 --> 01:09:19,500
 To je baš, baš velika stvar.

2454
01:09:19,500 --> 01:09:21,300
 A koliko je to ljudima

2455
01:09:21,300 --> 01:09:22,380
 kojima on dođe,

2456
01:09:22,480 --> 01:09:23,300
 pogotovo je s kršćanjem

2457
01:09:23,300 --> 01:09:24,060
 bilo progonjeni.

2458
01:09:24,060 --> 01:09:26,400
 Koliko to dadne snagu

2459
01:09:26,400 --> 01:09:27,240
 da izdržiš

2460
01:09:27,240 --> 01:09:28,360
 i budi ti nadu

2461
01:09:28,360 --> 01:09:29,760
 da će nekad to možda proć.

2462
01:09:29,760 --> 01:09:31,460
 Ono, izdržat će ovo,

2463
01:09:31,460 --> 01:09:32,220
 bit će bolje.

2464
01:09:32,220 --> 01:09:33,260
 Doće vrijeme mira,

2465
01:09:33,260 --> 01:09:34,320
 doće vrijeme kad će moć

2466
01:09:34,320 --> 01:09:36,340
 slobodno živiti svoju vjeru.

2467
01:09:36,340 --> 01:09:37,960
 Mi nismo ni svjesni toga

2468
01:09:37,960 --> 01:09:39,380
 koliko je papa zapravo važan

2469
01:09:39,380 --> 01:09:40,180
 tim nekim ljudima.

2470
01:09:40,180 --> 01:09:41,880
 Nama je dobro vamo.

2471
01:09:41,880 --> 01:09:44,000
 Mi možda pap toliko

2472
01:09:44,000 --> 01:09:45,380
 niskontamo nešto.

2473
01:09:45,380 --> 01:09:46,660
 Spravo možda zbog tog razgleda

2474
01:09:46,660 --> 01:09:47,960
 što nam i je tako dobro.

2475
01:09:47,960 --> 01:09:49,000
 Dok ne znam,

2476
01:09:49,060 --> 01:09:50,020
 nije dirnuo Međugorje,

2477
01:09:50,020 --> 01:09:50,800
 nismo ga niskontali.

2478
01:09:50,800 --> 01:09:51,760
 Kad je da Međugorje nešto super,

2479
01:09:51,760 --> 01:09:52,960
 onda je papa ekstra.

2480
01:09:52,960 --> 01:09:54,960
 Onda kad je dirniju Stepinca,

2481
01:09:54,960 --> 01:09:56,000
 a što mu je sad?

2482
01:09:56,000 --> 01:09:57,400
 Što mu bi?

2483
01:09:57,400 --> 01:09:58,560
 Što nas ne voli sad?

2484
01:09:58,560 --> 01:10:00,340
 Ono, kad te malo dirne,

2485
01:10:00,340 --> 01:10:01,560
 onda ga skontašo.

2486
01:10:01,560 --> 01:10:02,400
 Inače nam je super.

2487
01:10:02,400 --> 01:10:05,240
 A tim ljudima kojima dođe,

2488
01:10:05,240 --> 01:10:06,660
 koliko ti to puno znači.

2489
01:10:06,660 --> 01:10:08,560
 Tako da vjerujem da je njegova uloga

2490
01:10:08,560 --> 01:10:10,260
 puna veća ovoga što sam ne uspio

2491
01:10:10,260 --> 01:10:11,420
 sad reći svojim riječima

2492
01:10:11,420 --> 01:10:13,260
 ali što mi možemo naći na internetu.

2493
01:10:13,260 --> 01:10:15,600
 Dok papu možda ne susretneš osobno

2494
01:10:15,600 --> 01:10:16,520
 u nekom svom osobnom

2495
01:10:16,520 --> 01:10:17,600
 i problemu i jadu.

2496
01:10:17,600 --> 01:10:20,800
 Nešto kontak koliko je velike važan

2497
01:10:20,800 --> 01:10:21,620
 u tvom životu.

2498
01:10:21,620 --> 01:10:23,820
 Molimo nam je za njega svaki dan,

2499
01:10:23,820 --> 01:10:26,320
 ali dok za tebe nije osobno važan,

2500
01:10:26,320 --> 01:10:27,660
 ništa ga nešto živi,

2501
01:10:27,660 --> 01:10:28,500
 nešto posebno.

2502
01:10:29,060 --> 01:10:31,600
 To možda i ja mogao spomenutel sad

2503
01:10:31,600 --> 01:10:34,680
 dok je papa Franjo bio bolestan.

2504
01:10:34,680 --> 01:10:36,980
 Mi uvijek molimo nekako za papa,

2505
01:10:36,980 --> 01:10:38,380
 u Kronice sjetimo,

2506
01:10:38,380 --> 01:10:40,480
 sad ćemo izmoliti za papu Franjo,

2507
01:10:40,480 --> 01:10:41,660
 na papine nakane,

2508
01:10:41,660 --> 01:10:42,780
 za potrebe crkve,

2509
01:10:42,780 --> 01:10:45,760
 ali se to nekako površno.

2510
01:10:45,760 --> 01:10:47,620
 I tako ja osobno mogu reći

2511
01:10:47,620 --> 01:10:49,600
 dok je papa bio bolestan,

2512
01:10:49,600 --> 01:10:51,200
 kad malo više počmeš

2513
01:10:51,200 --> 01:10:52,360
 i molit za njega,

2514
01:10:52,360 --> 01:10:53,540
 za njegove zdravlje,

2515
01:10:53,540 --> 01:10:54,760
 da ga duh sveti i vodi,

2516
01:10:54,760 --> 01:10:57,300
 baš osjećaš puno veću povezanost s njim.

2517
01:10:57,300 --> 01:10:58,420
 Postanete blandraž.

2518
01:10:58,440 --> 01:11:00,260
 Zavoliš čovjeka,

2519
01:11:00,260 --> 01:11:00,720
 nisam ga nikad vidio,

2520
01:11:00,720 --> 01:11:01,320
 zavoliš ga.

2521
01:11:01,320 --> 01:11:03,520
 Prije toga ga ne primjećuješ,

2522
01:11:03,520 --> 01:11:06,040
 ali kad počneš moliti istinski za njegovno,

2523
01:11:06,040 --> 01:11:07,680
 priraste ti srce,

2524
01:11:07,680 --> 01:11:08,780
 postane ti drag čovjek.

2525
01:11:08,780 --> 01:11:10,340
 Promijenu se stvari u duši.

2526
01:11:10,340 --> 01:11:12,340
 Znaš, kako bi ja to nazval,

2527
01:11:12,340 --> 01:11:13,880
 možda neko duhovno prijateljstvo,

2528
01:11:13,880 --> 01:11:16,260
 jer ti kad nu riječ prijateljstvo,

2529
01:11:16,260 --> 01:11:17,720
 a mi koje sa latinskom prevedeš

2530
01:11:17,720 --> 01:11:19,780
 na hrvatski u direktnom smislu,

2531
01:11:19,780 --> 01:11:21,860
 znači čuvar duše.

2532
01:11:21,860 --> 01:11:24,160
 I ti kad za nekoga moliš,

2533
01:11:24,160 --> 01:11:25,340
 ti mu čuvaš dušu,

2534
01:11:25,400 --> 01:11:26,760
 od svega što na nju mora doći.

2535
01:11:26,760 --> 01:11:27,940
 A papa je vjerujen,

2536
01:11:27,940 --> 01:11:29,160
 je izložen svemu i svačemu.

2537
01:11:29,160 --> 01:11:31,180
 U prilikama je da učini sve i svašta,

2538
01:11:31,180 --> 01:11:33,660
 koliko za njega treba moliti.

2539
01:11:33,660 --> 01:11:34,960
 Tako čuvaš njegovu dušu,

2540
01:11:34,960 --> 01:11:35,960
 postoješ mu prijatelj.

2541
01:11:36,760 --> 01:11:38,540
 Tako da, vjerujem da je to zbog toga.

2542
01:11:38,540 --> 01:11:40,140
 Znači, postoji si blizak s njima

2543
01:11:40,140 --> 01:11:40,840
 da ne znaš kako,

2544
01:11:40,840 --> 01:11:41,880
 kroz malo to.

2545
01:11:41,880 --> 01:11:43,640
 A kako ti uopće malo,

2546
01:11:43,640 --> 01:11:45,000
 kako mišljen imaš,

2547
01:11:45,000 --> 01:11:46,340
 evo, papi, Franj,

2548
01:11:46,340 --> 01:11:48,460
 kako si ti doživio njegov pontifikat?

2549
01:11:48,460 --> 01:11:50,060
 Znaš šta ću ti reći,

2550
01:11:50,060 --> 01:11:50,920
 bit ću ovdje iskren.

2551
01:11:52,400 --> 01:11:54,140
 Nisam ga toliko doživljava

2552
01:11:54,140 --> 01:11:54,980
 dok nije umrao.

2553
01:11:54,980 --> 01:11:57,260
 Čudno, ali ono,

2554
01:11:57,260 --> 01:12:00,120
 neke stvari sam samopodrazumijevala.

2555
01:12:00,120 --> 01:12:01,400
 No, ok, ovaj, takav, to je to.

2556
01:12:01,400 --> 01:12:02,660
 A on kad je umra,

2557
01:12:02,660 --> 01:12:03,600
 kad se sva počeo

2558
01:12:03,600 --> 01:12:05,060
 skenirati stvari,

2559
01:12:05,060 --> 01:12:06,560
 šta je on zapravo sve uradio.

2560
01:12:06,560 --> 01:12:10,700
 Zašto nama u početku svima smetao?

2561
01:12:10,700 --> 01:12:12,780
 Jer je bio potpuno drugačiji

2562
01:12:12,780 --> 01:12:14,280
 od svi na koje smo mi navikli.

2563
01:12:14,280 --> 01:12:15,920
 Navikali smo na Ivana Pala II,

2564
01:12:15,920 --> 01:12:16,920
 navikali smo na Brnje Dikta,

2565
01:12:16,920 --> 01:12:18,500
 koji su opet bili

2566
01:12:18,500 --> 01:12:20,320
 imeđusobno različiti,

2567
01:12:20,320 --> 01:12:21,980
 ali opet različiti od njega.

2568
01:12:22,400 --> 01:12:25,660
 Unicrku otvorio sirom asmo,

2569
01:12:25,660 --> 01:12:27,240
 otvorio je dalekima,

2570
01:12:27,240 --> 01:12:30,120
 otvorio je svakom mogućem grešniku.

2571
01:12:30,120 --> 01:12:32,980
 I to što je,

2572
01:12:32,980 --> 01:12:35,020
 po meni, najveća sva koju je učinio,

2573
01:12:35,020 --> 01:12:36,560
 možda drugima to tako neće biti,

2574
01:12:36,560 --> 01:12:37,220
 ali meni je,

2575
01:12:37,220 --> 01:12:39,380
 kad je uvio 2016.

2576
01:12:39,380 --> 01:12:41,640
 koji je izvanredniji jubileje Milosrđa.

2577
01:12:41,640 --> 01:12:43,600
 Zato da ljudi Milosrđa

2578
01:12:43,600 --> 01:12:44,980
 nisu doživljavali nešto puno.

2579
01:12:44,980 --> 01:12:46,740
 Te se godine o tome

2580
01:12:46,740 --> 01:12:48,860
 bolam pričala i pričala i pričala.

2581
01:12:48,860 --> 01:12:50,800
 Svugdje se govorilo o tome.

2582
01:12:51,740 --> 01:12:52,760
 Pa smo tu skontali,

2583
01:12:52,760 --> 01:12:53,880
 barem ja,

2584
01:12:53,880 --> 01:12:56,380
 koliko je zapravo to bolje Milosrđa,

2585
01:12:56,380 --> 01:12:58,620
 jer je stvarno i neiscrpivo,

2586
01:12:58,620 --> 01:12:59,460
 neistraživo,

2587
01:12:59,460 --> 01:13:02,000
 i kako god doće što govori Faustina,

2588
01:13:02,000 --> 01:13:03,280
 sve one epitete,

2589
01:13:03,280 --> 01:13:06,420
 nedostavno ne moreš ga do kraja izreći.

2590
01:13:06,840 --> 01:13:10,100
 ja vjerujem da je to ta godina

2591
01:13:10,100 --> 01:13:13,420
 mnoge ljude vratila u crkvu.

2592
01:13:13,420 --> 01:13:15,340
 Mnoge ljude.

2593
01:13:15,340 --> 01:13:18,060
 Bilo da su se krstili,

2594
01:13:18,060 --> 01:13:19,640
 bilo da su neka bile krstini,

2595
01:13:19,640 --> 01:13:22,700
 pa se sad sam pomovo vratili životu sakramentalno.

2596
01:13:23,480 --> 01:13:26,460
 a vjerujem da je to skinulo jako puno tereta,

2597
01:13:26,460 --> 01:13:28,300
 jako puno savjesti,

2598
01:13:28,300 --> 01:13:29,980
 odstavno jako puno duša,

2599
01:13:29,980 --> 01:13:32,880
 koje su se bojale i osude i straha,

2600
01:13:32,880 --> 01:13:35,340
 i ne znam nija čega sve ono u toj ispovijedi.

2601
01:13:36,500 --> 01:13:39,060
 iznosno su otišli ljudi tamo da se rasterete

2602
01:13:39,060 --> 01:13:40,740
 i naišli su na oslobođenje.

2603
01:13:40,740 --> 01:13:42,820
 I ja vjerujem da je ta stvar,

2604
01:13:42,820 --> 01:13:43,520
 ta godina,

2605
01:13:43,520 --> 01:13:46,500
 njegov pontifikat učinila jako velikim.

2606
01:13:46,500 --> 01:13:49,080
 Uz sve druge stvari,

2607
01:13:49,080 --> 01:13:51,480
 koje je proglasno za dan bolesnika,

2608
01:13:51,480 --> 01:13:53,440
 dan starih baka i djedova,

2609
01:13:53,440 --> 01:13:54,280
 dan djece,

2610
01:13:54,280 --> 01:13:57,600
 enciklike koje potišnu na razmišljanje

2611
01:13:57,600 --> 01:13:59,340
 o našem okruženju,

2612
01:13:59,340 --> 01:14:00,800
 o svijetu u kojem živimo,

2613
01:14:00,800 --> 01:14:02,340
 o zajednjištu međusobno.

2614
01:14:02,340 --> 01:14:04,440
 Neke stvari koje je učinio

2615
01:14:04,440 --> 01:14:06,260
 na području zakonodavstva crkve

2616
01:14:06,260 --> 01:14:08,340
 bilo je tu jako finih potjez,

2617
01:14:08,340 --> 01:14:09,700
 jako finih posjeta.

2618
01:14:09,700 --> 01:14:11,820
 Ne znam to što je se prvi put

2619
01:14:11,820 --> 01:14:13,160
 u tisuću godina susreo

2620
01:14:13,160 --> 01:14:15,480
 sa patrijarhom pravoslavne crkve

2621
01:14:15,480 --> 01:14:16,160
 u Rusiji.

2622
01:14:16,160 --> 01:14:18,240
 I papa je koji u džamiju ušao.

2623
01:14:18,240 --> 01:14:19,140
 Tako je.

2624
01:14:19,140 --> 01:14:22,240
 Jako puno stvari koje je učinio

2625
01:14:22,240 --> 01:14:23,480
 kao prvi put u povijesti

2626
01:14:23,480 --> 01:14:25,280
 ili nakon dugo vremena u povijesti.

2627
01:14:25,280 --> 01:14:28,000
 Tako da je pontifikat

2628
01:14:28,000 --> 01:14:29,600
 možda nauko kratak,

2629
01:14:29,600 --> 01:14:31,960
 ali vjerujem da nismo još do kraja

2630
01:14:31,960 --> 01:14:32,960
 ni svjesni posjedica

2631
01:14:32,960 --> 01:14:35,320
 koju će se god potom je pontifikat.

2632
01:14:36,020 --> 01:14:36,960
 Tako da ono,

2633
01:14:36,960 --> 01:14:39,120
 kad je umro sam postao svjestan čovječe.

2634
01:14:39,120 --> 01:14:40,680
 Koliko je stvari radio.

2635
01:14:40,680 --> 01:14:42,200
 Koliko je, recimo na meditaciju

2636
01:14:42,200 --> 01:14:42,940
 njegova u koroni

2637
01:14:42,940 --> 01:14:43,500
 kad je imao

2638
01:14:43,500 --> 01:14:45,960
 malo vjerni.

2639
01:14:45,960 --> 01:14:47,100
 Zašto ste posumnjali?

2640
01:14:47,100 --> 01:14:48,620
 Ono, kad je imao večer

2641
01:14:48,620 --> 01:14:50,100
 pred Bazilikom.

2642
01:14:51,160 --> 01:14:54,060
 gdje nas ono, puno ljudi se urazalo u sjećanje.

2643
01:14:54,060 --> 01:14:56,680
 Da se nekad barem sjetite toga ponovo.

2644
01:14:56,680 --> 01:14:58,200
 Hrabro, sama ne bojte.

2645
01:14:58,200 --> 01:14:59,080
 Ja sam s vama.

2646
01:14:59,080 --> 01:15:02,240
 Koliko je to bila fina gesta.

2647
01:15:02,240 --> 01:15:04,180
 Da ljudima koji su u strahu

2648
01:15:04,180 --> 01:15:05,160
 od nečega što ne poznaju,

2649
01:15:05,160 --> 01:15:06,800
 da im vrati pouzanje u Boga.

2650
01:15:07,440 --> 01:15:08,580
 Okej, boj će ti toga,

2651
01:15:08,580 --> 01:15:10,420
 ali uzavljaj sobu ga će biti dobro.

2652
01:15:10,420 --> 01:15:12,220
 Koliko je to velika stvar.

2653
01:15:12,220 --> 01:15:14,360
 Baš nas je on malo i

2654
01:15:14,360 --> 01:15:16,500
 na neki način isprovocirao

2655
01:15:16,500 --> 01:15:18,460
 s tim što je bio drugačiji.

2656
01:15:18,460 --> 01:15:19,620
 I siromaštvom,

2657
01:15:19,620 --> 01:15:20,540
 i panizno jošću,

2658
01:15:20,540 --> 01:15:21,680
 i time baš te ono nekad...

2659
01:15:21,680 --> 01:15:24,740
 Iša je na margini družbaš mu...

2660
01:15:24,740 --> 01:15:27,220
 Baš je služio tom imenu Franja.

2661
01:15:27,220 --> 01:15:31,480
 Najvalike četvrtak on pere noge u zatvoru.

2662
01:15:31,480 --> 01:15:34,760
 Mislim da sam osvrstvo ne sjećan da se ikad je vidio

2663
01:15:34,760 --> 01:15:35,740
 nekoliko sjećanika,

2664
01:15:35,740 --> 01:15:38,760
 da je ono pap pogotovo da je išao u zatvor

2665
01:15:38,760 --> 01:15:40,420
 dok Franja nisam vidio.

2666
01:15:40,420 --> 01:15:42,320
 Moguće da su prije išli.

2667
01:15:42,320 --> 01:15:43,740
 Ne, ne kaže ja da nisi,

2668
01:15:43,740 --> 01:15:44,840
 ja osvrstvo nisam vidio.

2669
01:15:44,840 --> 01:15:47,220
 Ja isto nisam zapratio da je,

2670
01:15:47,220 --> 01:15:49,720
 dok on i on je neprostavno višao k njima.

2671
01:15:50,520 --> 01:15:52,280
 Čak sam mislim da sam prošto negdje da je

2672
01:15:52,280 --> 01:15:54,340
 na tjednoj razini volio otići u zatvor,

2673
01:15:54,340 --> 01:15:55,800
 tamo kod njih biti,

2674
01:15:55,800 --> 01:15:57,380
 ispovjeti nekoga koja treba slaviti,

2675
01:15:57,380 --> 01:15:59,020
 s nima mislu da mu je to bilo nešto

2676
01:15:59,020 --> 01:16:00,080
 do čega je baš držao.

2677
01:16:00,080 --> 01:16:02,480
 Možda sam prošto krije pratar,

2678
01:16:02,480 --> 01:16:03,920
 ali tako mi je ostalo u glavi.

2679
01:16:03,920 --> 01:16:06,060
 Tako da ovo uzme to ono kongranosalis.

2680
01:16:06,060 --> 01:16:09,860
 Glavno, volio je posjećivati takve ljude,

2681
01:16:09,860 --> 01:16:12,920
 domove, ono, nezbrinutom djecom je to.

2682
01:16:12,920 --> 01:16:15,040
 On je baš na rubu društva.

2683
01:16:15,040 --> 01:16:15,580
 Da, išao je baš na rubu.

2684
01:16:15,580 --> 01:16:21,800
 On je ostalo u nas svako malo,

2685
01:16:21,800 --> 01:16:24,040
 možda zbog medijske prezentacije,

2686
01:16:24,040 --> 01:16:27,020
 malo u nekom negativnom svijetu,

2687
01:16:27,020 --> 01:16:29,600
 zbog, rećemo tog, navodno, liberalizma,

2688
01:16:29,600 --> 01:16:31,960
 ali koliko je baš u tom istine,

2689
01:16:31,960 --> 01:16:34,460
 ili je to sve medijski naslovi, priče.

2690
01:16:35,540 --> 01:16:38,120
 Pa ja vjerujem da u nas može biti krivi prijevoda,

2691
01:16:38,120 --> 01:16:40,780
 može biti jako puno krivi tumačene,

2692
01:16:40,780 --> 01:16:42,320
 izvlačene stvari iz konteksta.

2693
01:16:42,320 --> 01:16:43,780
 I senzacionalističkih naslova,

2694
01:16:43,780 --> 01:16:44,880
 i da ljudi uopće ne idu.

2695
01:16:44,880 --> 01:16:45,500
 No, naravno.

2696
01:16:45,500 --> 01:16:47,620
 Ono, ne znam, čovjek je zekljen 10 rečenica,

2697
01:16:47,620 --> 01:16:48,960
 njesto ga izvukao dvih riječi,

2698
01:16:48,960 --> 01:16:50,740
 koje ste pasali, staviliš to kao naslo,

2699
01:16:50,740 --> 01:16:51,680
 papa rekao to.

2700
01:16:51,680 --> 01:16:53,700
 E, najviše se to vezalo za ovaj

2701
01:16:53,700 --> 01:16:56,260
 blagoslov istospolnih parova.

2702
01:16:56,260 --> 01:16:57,480
 Parova i toga svega naravno.

2703
01:16:57,480 --> 01:16:59,120
 Sjećam se o jednog intervjua,

2704
01:16:59,120 --> 01:17:01,500
 njega novinarka Pita,

2705
01:17:01,500 --> 01:17:04,140
 evo, vi ste nedavno dopustili blagoslov

2706
01:17:04,140 --> 01:17:07,020
 istospolnih parova, zajednica,

2707
01:17:07,020 --> 01:17:09,580
 ono, no, odmah u startu je demantira,

2708
01:17:09,580 --> 01:17:11,380
 ne, nisam to dopustio,

2709
01:17:11,380 --> 01:17:13,000
 krivo ste to prenijeli,

2710
01:17:13,000 --> 01:17:14,380
 krivo ste to interpretirali,

2711
01:17:14,380 --> 01:17:17,520
 ja sam dopustio blagoslov tih osoba,

2712
01:17:17,520 --> 01:17:21,320
 jer, onaj, može meni doći neki poslodavac,

2713
01:17:21,320 --> 01:17:23,540
 koji, ne znam, izrabljuje radnike,

2714
01:17:23,540 --> 01:17:25,920
 koji radi možda veći grijeh nego tih osoba,

2715
01:17:25,980 --> 01:17:27,400
 i da ja njemu dadnem blagoslov,

2716
01:17:27,400 --> 01:17:29,260
 a ovoj drugoj osobi neće.

2717
01:17:29,260 --> 01:17:31,640
 Dakle, ja vjerujem da je on činio

2718
01:17:31,640 --> 01:17:33,500
 ono što je činio i sveti Franjo,

2719
01:17:33,500 --> 01:17:35,640
 a zgrančio je grijeh od grešnika.

2720
01:17:35,640 --> 01:17:38,820
 Franjo je isto oko Isus,

2721
01:17:38,820 --> 01:17:39,840
 mrzi i grijeh.

2722
01:17:39,840 --> 01:17:43,100
 Nije mu drago, grijeh nijednog grešnika,

2723
01:17:43,100 --> 01:17:45,700
 ali znao bi je zbog toga

2724
01:17:45,700 --> 01:17:47,240
 ne osudit grešnika,

2725
01:17:47,240 --> 01:17:50,260
 osudio bi grijeh da ne volja blud,

2726
01:17:50,260 --> 01:17:52,420
 ali nije rekao bludniku da je gotov.

2727
01:17:52,420 --> 01:17:54,840
 I mislim da je tu papa

2728
01:17:54,840 --> 01:17:56,720
 na takve stvari mislio,

2729
01:17:56,720 --> 01:17:58,040
 blagoslovi grešnika.

2730
01:17:58,040 --> 01:18:00,700
 Možda mu pomogne da postane bolji,

2731
01:18:00,700 --> 01:18:02,580
 da vidje da ima nade za njega,

2732
01:18:02,580 --> 01:18:04,220
 da ga ni crkva nije napustila,

2733
01:18:04,220 --> 01:18:05,300
 ni Boga nije zaboravio.

2734
01:18:06,200 --> 01:18:08,340
 ali grijeh je kao takav nikad.

2735
01:18:08,340 --> 01:18:09,900
 Možda je na to mislio,

2736
01:18:09,900 --> 01:18:11,980
 samo sudi krivo protumačili,

2737
01:18:11,980 --> 01:18:13,500
 ne znam kako paše ljudima,

2738
01:18:13,500 --> 01:18:15,080
 pogotovo današnjim medijima,

2739
01:18:15,080 --> 01:18:16,420
 paše im tako,

2740
01:18:16,420 --> 01:18:17,560
 pa evo stavit ćemo tu,

2741
01:18:17,560 --> 01:18:20,020
 i tako i nadobio što dobiješ,

2742
01:18:20,020 --> 01:18:20,440
 to je to.

2743
01:18:20,440 --> 01:18:23,160
 To je vjerojatno ljudima im ponaviše za smetalo,

2744
01:18:23,160 --> 01:18:26,100
 zbog pa naše same tvrdoće srca,

2745
01:18:26,100 --> 01:18:28,120
 evo što mi možda je prvo vidimo grijeha,

2746
01:18:28,120 --> 01:18:29,220
 ne vidimo griješnika,

2747
01:18:29,220 --> 01:18:30,720
 ne vidimo čovjeka ispred sebe,

2748
01:18:30,720 --> 01:18:31,020
 koja možda...

2749
01:18:31,020 --> 01:18:32,120
 Kad se radi u nama,

2750
01:18:32,120 --> 01:18:33,760
 rozgrančimo to jako dobro,

2751
01:18:33,760 --> 01:18:34,900
 uzimamo pincetu,

2752
01:18:34,900 --> 01:18:35,860
 pa rastavljamo stvari,

2753
01:18:35,860 --> 01:18:37,560
 koliko daleko možemo ići,

2754
01:18:37,560 --> 01:18:39,400
 a odrugom zašiš toč,

2755
01:18:39,400 --> 01:18:41,280
 vršće moraš da se nemoji uopće rastaviti.

2756
01:18:41,280 --> 01:18:44,680
 Ali evo, kako reagirati u tim slučajima,

2757
01:18:44,680 --> 01:18:46,420
 kad se mi ne slažemo s papom,

2758
01:18:46,420 --> 01:18:46,920
 evo,

2759
01:18:46,920 --> 01:18:49,940
 ne je nužno sad vezi toga,

2760
01:18:49,940 --> 01:18:50,580
 ali evo, ne znam,

2761
01:18:50,580 --> 01:18:51,900
 evo, bile i cijepljeni,

2762
01:18:51,900 --> 01:18:53,380
 te stvari, te gluposti,

2763
01:18:53,380 --> 01:18:54,540
 da ne pričamo o tome,

2764
01:18:54,540 --> 01:18:55,780
 ali, nego evo,

2765
01:18:55,780 --> 01:18:59,000
 trebamo mi vjerovati u sve što papa govori.

2766
01:18:59,360 --> 01:19:01,600
 Dakle, postoje stvari koje su obvezne za vjerovat.

2767
01:19:01,600 --> 01:19:02,440
 To je nauka,

2768
01:19:02,440 --> 01:19:03,180
 to je katolička crkva,

2769
01:19:03,180 --> 01:19:03,980
 to su dogme,

2770
01:19:03,980 --> 01:19:05,080
 to je sve to pismo,

2771
01:19:05,080 --> 01:19:06,300
 ono što je Bog izrako.

2772
01:19:06,300 --> 01:19:08,720
 Papine stvari,

2773
01:19:08,720 --> 01:19:10,220
 pa ono što papa govori,

2774
01:19:10,220 --> 01:19:12,100
 može biti savjet,

2775
01:19:12,100 --> 01:19:14,580
 možete potaknuti na razmišljanje,

2776
01:19:14,580 --> 01:19:18,000
 ja i ti ne moramo razmišljati s to nekim stvarima.

2777
01:19:18,000 --> 01:19:19,460
 Niti mene,

2778
01:19:19,460 --> 01:19:22,640
 tvoje razmišljanje obvezuje da ja to prihvatim kao istinu,

2779
01:19:22,640 --> 01:19:27,020
 ali niti me to poziva na to da ja tebi dokazujem da to tvoje nije istina,

2780
01:19:27,020 --> 01:19:28,520
 pa da te uvjeravam,

2781
01:19:28,520 --> 01:19:29,680
 me to ti nije dobro,

2782
01:19:29,680 --> 01:19:30,600
 tako misli to ono,

2783
01:19:30,600 --> 01:19:31,500
 da zbog ovoga ili ovoga,

2784
01:19:31,500 --> 01:19:32,420
 to ne.

2785
01:19:32,420 --> 01:19:34,720
 Tako isto imam pravo i ja,

2786
01:19:34,720 --> 01:19:36,220
 imam dar razuma,

2787
01:19:36,220 --> 01:19:38,100
 dao mi ga je Bog po duhu svijetom,

2788
01:19:38,100 --> 01:19:40,560
 da razmišljam o stvarima koje čujem,

2789
01:19:40,560 --> 01:19:42,300
 kako što je izrako papa,

2790
01:19:42,300 --> 01:19:43,400
 da ako je bilo kod drugi,

2791
01:19:43,400 --> 01:19:45,140
 mogu razmišljati o tome,

2792
01:19:45,140 --> 01:19:48,280
 naću tome za sebe nešto dobro i koristno,

2793
01:19:48,360 --> 01:19:50,560
 nešto što meni ne koristi pa ću odbaciti.

2794
01:19:50,560 --> 01:19:55,200
 Ono što moram slušati i vjerovati je su ako papa naučava nešto iz evanđelja,

2795
01:19:55,200 --> 01:19:56,800
 nešto iz nauka crkve,

2796
01:19:56,800 --> 01:19:58,780
 ok, to moram ispreman poslušati.

2797
01:20:00,040 --> 01:20:02,220
 Ako je to nešto što se meni uopće ne tiče,

2798
01:20:02,220 --> 01:20:03,800
 zašto ću to uopći komentirati?

2799
01:20:03,800 --> 01:20:06,800
 Ako je uputio riječ nekom zatvoreniku,

2800
01:20:06,800 --> 01:20:08,380
 vezano za njegov život,

2801
01:20:08,380 --> 01:20:10,320
 što ću ja to gledat,

2802
01:20:10,320 --> 01:20:11,160
 da mene dira,

2803
01:20:11,160 --> 01:20:13,100
 ako se ja s tim ne slažem,

2804
01:20:13,100 --> 01:20:14,840
 kada to se mene ne tiče,

2805
01:20:14,840 --> 01:20:16,260
 neću razgovarati o tome,

2806
01:20:16,260 --> 01:20:19,820
 ono, je to tebe žena kaže neke stvari što su važne za,

2807
01:20:19,820 --> 01:20:21,200
 ne znam, ono,

2808
01:20:21,200 --> 01:20:24,380
 bilo kodat kaže neke stvari za tvoju odnos nekim.

2809
01:20:24,380 --> 01:20:26,440
 Što se to mene tiče, druže?

2810
01:20:26,440 --> 01:20:28,580
 Apsolutno ništa, to je vaša stvara,

2811
01:20:28,680 --> 01:20:30,560
 vi rješavajte, mene se ne dira.

2812
01:20:30,560 --> 01:20:32,860
 Ono što moram uzeti k sebi,

2813
01:20:32,860 --> 01:20:34,640
 vidite, ako me neka priječ potekne

2814
01:20:34,640 --> 01:20:36,860
 da mi kopa savijest,

2815
01:20:36,860 --> 01:20:37,900
 da mi stvara nemirno savijest,

2816
01:20:37,900 --> 01:20:39,060
 znači nešto tu dobro ima,

2817
01:20:39,060 --> 01:20:42,140
 što je mene negdje našao neki moj trnu duši

2818
01:20:42,140 --> 01:20:44,060
 da moram izvaziti, pa me to malo kopka,

2819
01:20:44,060 --> 01:20:45,660
 tu ću, to te vidit ću.

2820
01:20:45,660 --> 01:20:47,560
 Što se događa, zašto mene to dira?

2821
01:20:47,560 --> 01:20:49,080
 Pa ću pokušati

2822
01:20:49,080 --> 01:20:51,960
 primijeniti te stvari koje papa govori,

2823
01:20:51,960 --> 01:20:53,020
 da mene bude bolje.

2824
01:20:53,020 --> 01:20:54,960
 Nekad je tako, nekad je tako zna prozvat,

2825
01:20:55,740 --> 01:20:58,100
 da i ne zna da je prozvat, pa se to dira,

2826
01:20:58,100 --> 01:20:59,960
 kopkate, stvarati nemir,

2827
01:20:59,960 --> 01:21:01,940
 da kao iskonto, čovjek je bio pravo.

2828
01:21:01,940 --> 01:21:03,820
 Nadak što vam ga prikrižiti,

2829
01:21:03,820 --> 01:21:05,960
 reći, ovaj liberan govori sve i sva šta,

2830
01:21:05,960 --> 01:21:06,860
 pa ću ga prikrižiti.

2831
01:21:07,360 --> 01:21:10,200
 Da, malo su povištne te naše priče,

2832
01:21:10,200 --> 01:21:12,960
 tim podjelama tradicionalnosti i liberalci.

2833
01:21:12,960 --> 01:21:14,220
 Dobro je dat priliku, ako ništa,

2834
01:21:14,220 --> 01:21:16,740
 pomolite se Bogu, pa vidit ću što mi Bog kaže

2835
01:21:16,740 --> 01:21:18,760
 na osnovu toga što sam čuo, što je papa rekao,

2836
01:21:18,760 --> 01:21:20,240
 možda baš bude meni korisno.

2837
01:21:20,240 --> 01:21:21,960
 Nikad ne znaš.

2838
01:21:21,960 --> 01:21:23,900
 Što kaže Nina Badrić,

2839
01:21:23,900 --> 01:21:25,860
 Bog krivom crtom piše pravo.

2840
01:21:25,860 --> 01:21:28,900
 A što mislimo po tim

2841
01:21:28,900 --> 01:21:30,640
 da duh sveti vodi crkvu?

2842
01:21:31,640 --> 01:21:33,460
 Isto ovo što je u konkluarama se vidilo.

2843
01:21:33,460 --> 01:21:36,280
 Čovjek je sanjao jednove.

2844
01:21:36,280 --> 01:21:37,580
 Svi su spominjali ti destine

2845
01:21:37,580 --> 01:21:38,860
 na koje smo spominjali malo prije.

2846
01:21:38,860 --> 01:21:41,520
 Na kraju je izašao jedanisti.

2847
01:21:41,520 --> 01:21:44,860
 To da duh sveti je vodi crkvu

2848
01:21:44,860 --> 01:21:46,740
 znači da Isusova, kad je rekao

2849
01:21:46,740 --> 01:21:48,440
 da je vrata pakljena,

2850
01:21:48,440 --> 01:21:50,040
 neće nam vadati stvarno istina.

2851
01:21:50,040 --> 01:21:51,780
 Je da je vodi čovjek.

2852
01:21:51,780 --> 01:21:54,280
 Isto kod svaka druga firma

2853
01:21:54,280 --> 01:21:55,100
 propala bi

2854
01:21:55,100 --> 01:21:57,600
 u roku dva pokoljenja.

2855
01:21:57,600 --> 01:22:01,180
 A ovo je 267. papa.

2856
01:22:01,640 --> 01:22:03,560
 Dakle dosad smo joj mogli pokovati

2857
01:22:03,560 --> 01:22:04,920
 267 puta.

2858
01:22:04,920 --> 01:22:07,620
 I bilo je papa svakakvi znaš

2859
01:22:07,620 --> 01:22:09,400
 i ti čitali smo danas

2860
01:22:09,400 --> 01:22:10,160
 i istraživali sam.

2861
01:22:10,160 --> 01:22:11,400
 Bilo je svega i svačega.

2862
01:22:11,400 --> 01:22:13,520
 Stvari da se pokriješ ti

2863
01:22:13,520 --> 01:22:14,340
 da mi je bilo.

2864
01:22:14,340 --> 01:22:16,080
 Bilo je papa antisemita

2865
01:22:16,080 --> 01:22:16,960
 što su pravili

2866
01:22:16,960 --> 01:22:19,440
 geto za židove u Rimu,

2867
01:22:19,440 --> 01:22:20,460
 bludnika.

2868
01:22:20,460 --> 01:22:22,160
 Pravili i bordele u crkvi.

2869
01:22:22,160 --> 01:22:25,040
 Vatikan je bio bordele jedno vrime.

2870
01:22:25,040 --> 01:22:26,680
 Šta da ti govorim?

2871
01:22:26,680 --> 01:22:28,220
 Bilo je papa ubojica

2872
01:22:28,220 --> 01:22:29,760
 jer je neko drugi metapa bi ubojili.

2873
01:22:30,480 --> 01:22:32,320
 imali su svoji dici pa su njihova djeca

2874
01:22:32,320 --> 01:22:33,240
 postavljali pape.

2875
01:22:33,240 --> 01:22:35,960
 Moramo tako nabrajati grijehe crkve.

2876
01:22:35,960 --> 01:22:37,680
 Sto je pan šesti koji je prethodnik

2877
01:22:37,680 --> 01:22:39,900
 krisko posudio ga ponovo.

2878
01:22:39,900 --> 01:22:41,640
 Stavio ga na sudašku stolicu.

2879
01:22:41,640 --> 01:22:43,120
 On se branio šutnju

2880
01:22:43,120 --> 01:22:45,300
 i sudio ga opet naspred.

2881
01:22:45,300 --> 01:22:46,900
 Odrazom u tri prsta,

2882
01:22:46,900 --> 01:22:47,780
 vratio ga u urob,

2883
01:22:47,780 --> 01:22:48,880
 opet ga izvadio,

2884
01:22:48,880 --> 01:22:49,940
 opet ga osudio

2885
01:22:49,940 --> 01:22:50,940
 i bacio ga u tiber.

2886
01:22:51,760 --> 01:22:53,380
 na bilo je jako puno stvari.

2887
01:22:53,380 --> 01:22:54,600
 Ali možda je upravo...

2888
01:22:54,600 --> 01:22:56,080
 A nego i dalje je živa.

2889
01:22:56,080 --> 01:22:57,860
 Upravo je to možda dokaz

2890
01:22:57,860 --> 01:22:59,640
 da je vrata paklona

2891
01:22:59,640 --> 01:23:00,500
 neće nadvladiti.

2892
01:23:00,500 --> 01:23:02,360
 Nedavno mi je to izletilo

2893
01:23:02,360 --> 01:23:03,600
 na Instagramu.

2894
01:23:03,600 --> 01:23:04,380
 Kaže,

2895
01:23:04,380 --> 01:23:07,960
 prikazuje tog svetog Petra.

2896
01:23:07,960 --> 01:23:08,920
 Kaže,

2897
01:23:08,920 --> 01:23:10,740
 ovdje je 67. godine

2898
01:23:10,740 --> 01:23:11,320
 Neron

2899
01:23:11,320 --> 01:23:13,020
 pogubio Petra.

2900
01:23:13,020 --> 01:23:15,380
 Da bi mu zatrio ime.

2901
01:23:15,380 --> 01:23:17,720
 Da bi ugasio crku.

2902
01:23:17,720 --> 01:23:19,760
 Neron danas prah,

2903
01:23:19,760 --> 01:23:20,300
 pepeo,

2904
01:23:20,300 --> 01:23:21,820
 crkva još u ovih stoji.

2905
01:23:21,820 --> 01:23:23,540
 A na crkvu ne stoji

2906
01:23:23,540 --> 01:23:24,980
 crkva zato što je ljudi drže.

2907
01:23:24,980 --> 01:23:26,840
 Jer ljudi su,

2908
01:23:26,840 --> 01:23:28,880
 znamo kako smo pokvareni.

2909
01:23:28,880 --> 01:23:30,620
 Skloni svemu i svačemu.

2910
01:23:30,620 --> 01:23:31,860
 Srce čovjekova ne mora

2911
01:23:31,860 --> 01:23:32,900
 zadovoljiti nikoj nego Bog.

2912
01:23:32,900 --> 01:23:34,620
 Srića pa je on tu,

2913
01:23:34,620 --> 01:23:35,900
 u njega se pita sve.

2914
01:23:35,900 --> 01:23:37,340
 Drži stvari na okupu.

2915
01:23:37,340 --> 01:23:40,620
 Uvijek upravlja sve ime.

2916
01:23:40,860 --> 01:23:42,500
 Dakle da nije toga,

2917
01:23:42,500 --> 01:23:44,100
 davno bi se ono srušilo,

2918
01:23:44,100 --> 01:23:45,520
 davno bi ljudi od toga

2919
01:23:45,520 --> 01:23:47,040
 napravili kuću trgovačku,

2920
01:23:47,040 --> 01:23:49,000
 a ne kuću di se Bog moli.

2921
01:23:49,000 --> 01:23:50,080
 Dakle da,

2922
01:23:50,080 --> 01:23:51,400
 Mirina je dokazao

2923
01:23:51,400 --> 01:23:51,700
 ko nas,

2924
01:23:51,700 --> 01:23:52,940
 ja puno ko želimo biti.

2925
01:23:52,940 --> 01:23:53,660
 Ako ne želimo,

2926
01:23:53,660 --> 01:23:54,760
 džaba da upirem prstom

2927
01:23:54,760 --> 01:23:55,800
 neko neće biti.

2928
01:23:55,800 --> 01:23:57,100
 Evo,

2929
01:23:57,100 --> 01:23:58,660
 već smo malo se dotakli

2930
01:23:58,660 --> 01:23:59,900
 molitve za papu

2931
01:23:59,900 --> 01:24:01,680
 i važnosti molitve

2932
01:24:01,680 --> 01:24:02,060
 jer on,

2933
01:24:02,060 --> 01:24:04,520
 na njegovim je leđima

2934
01:24:04,520 --> 01:24:05,400
 cijela crkva.

2935
01:24:05,400 --> 01:24:06,440
 Sav teret.

2936
01:24:06,440 --> 01:24:07,300
 Sav teret,

2937
01:24:07,300 --> 01:24:09,060
 ono nije čast,

2938
01:24:09,060 --> 01:24:09,940
 ono nije vlast,

2939
01:24:09,940 --> 01:24:10,400
 ono je

2940
01:24:10,400 --> 01:24:11,740
 služba,

2941
01:24:11,740 --> 01:24:12,440
 žrtva,

2942
01:24:12,440 --> 01:24:13,180
 patnja,

2943
01:24:13,180 --> 01:24:13,960
 odbačeno,

2944
01:24:13,960 --> 01:24:15,200
 samoća i bol.

2945
01:24:15,200 --> 01:24:16,580
 I ja sam rekao opet

2946
01:24:16,580 --> 01:24:17,600
 žrtva treba reći.

2947
01:24:17,600 --> 01:24:17,900
 Dakle,

2948
01:24:17,900 --> 01:24:18,680
 ništa drugo.

2949
01:24:18,680 --> 01:24:20,360
 Onda nema ni časti

